{"title_page": "2007 Santiago Wanderers season", "text_new": "{{Orphan|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox football club season\n|club               = [[Club de Deportes Santiago Wanderers|Santiago Wanderers]]\n|season             = [[2007 Primera Divisi\u00f3n of Chile|2007]]\n|image              = \n|image_size         = \n|alt                = \n|caption            = \n|chrtitle           = President\n|chairman           = {{flagicon|CHI}} Carlos Bombal\n|mgrtitle           = Coaches\n|manager            = {{flagicon|CHI}} Hern\u00e1n Godoy {{small|(Apertura)}}<br>{{flagicon|CHI}} [[Yuri Fern\u00e1ndez]]  {{small|(Clausura)}}\n|stadium            = [[Estadio El\u00edas Figueroa Brander|Estadio Regional Chiledeportes]]\n|league             = Torneo Apertura\n|league result      = [[2007 Torneo Apertura (Chile)|20th]]\n|league2            = Torneo Clausura\n|league2 result     = [[2007 Torneo Clausura (Chile)|5th]] (Regular stage)\n|cup1               = \n|cup1 result        = \n|league topscorer   = \n|season topscorer   = \n|highest attendance = \n|lowest attendance  = \n|average attendance = \n|largest win        = \n|largest loss       = \n|pattern_la1        = _whiteborder\n|pattern_b1         = _whitecollarplain\n|pattern_ra1        = _whiteborder\n|pattern_sh1        = \n|pattern_so1        = _3whitehoops\n|leftarm1           = 1b4125\n|body1              = 1b4125\n|rightarm1          = 1b4125\n|shorts1            = FFFFFF\n|socks1             = 1b4125\n|alt1               = \n|filetype1          = \n|pattern_la2        = _greenborder\n|pattern_b2         = _greenleftsash\n|pattern_ra2        = _greenborder\n|pattern_sh2        = \n|pattern_so2        = _hoops_green_2\n|leftarm2           = FFFFFF\n|body2              = FFFFFF\n|rightarm2          = FFFFFF\n|shorts2            = 1b4125\n|socks2             = FFFFFF\n|alt2               = \n|filetype2          = \n|updated            = \n|prevseason         = 2006\n|nextseason         = 2008\n}}\nThe 2007 season is Santiago Wanderers 81st season in the [[Chilean Primera Divisi\u00f3n|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] and 44th in the Campeonato Nacional. This article shows player statistics and all matches (official and friendly) that the club played during the 2007 season.\n\nIn a season made to commemorate its 115th anniversary, the club had a poor performance during the year, by finishing the Torneo Apertura in 20th position with 13 points and the Torneo Clausura in 5th place of the Group A with 17 points. As a consequence, Santiago Wanderers was relegated to Primera B for the 2008 season, after finishing the year table in 20th position with 30 points.<ref>{{cite book |title=Memoria Anual 2007 |date=2008 |publisher=Corporaci\u00f3n Club de Deportes Santiago Wanderers |location=Valpara\u00edso |page=13 |url=http://www.corporacionwanderers.cl/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2007-Memoria-Corporaci%C3%B3n-Santiago-Wanderers.pdf |accessdate=13 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Squad==\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=2|nat=CHI|name=[[Christian G\u00e1lvez (footballer)|Christian G\u00e1lvez]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=3|nat=CHI|name=[[Juan Robledo]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=4|nat=CHI|name=[[Franco Salinas]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=CHI|name=[[Sebastian Mendez Plaza|Sebastian M\u00e9ndez]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=CHI|name=[[Roberto Luco]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=7|nat=CHI|name=[[Paulo P\u00e9rez]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=8|nat=CHI|name=[[Victor Quintanilla]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=9|nat=CHI|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Alberto Soto]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=CHI|name=[[Miguel Catal\u00e1n]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=CHI|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Luis Jim\u00e9nez]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=CHI|name=[[Hern\u00e1n Godoy]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=15|nat=PAR|name=[[Victor Hugo Avalos]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=CHI|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Catalan]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=CHI|name=[[Mauricio Tampe]]|pos=MF|}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=CHI|name=[[Juan Silva (Chilean footballer, born 1989)|Juan Silva]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=ARG|name=[[Luis Alberto Benitez]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=CHI|name=[[Jaime Grondona]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=CHI|name=[[Martin Fabbro]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=CHI|name=[[Michael Silva]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=24|nat=CHI|name=[[Sebasti\u00e1n Roco]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=25|nat=CHI|name=[[Francisco Prieto]]|pos=GK|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=29|nat=CHI|name=[[Eric Godoy]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=30|nat=CHI|name=[[Francisco Arancibia]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=32|nat=CHI|name=[[David Reyes]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Competitions==\n===Torneo Apertura===\n{{see also|2007 Torneo Apertura (Chile)}}\n\n====Standings====\n{{:2007 Torneo Apertura (Chile)|transcludesection=League table|showteam=SAW|show_limit=5}}\n\n====Matches====\n{{legend2|#CCFFCC|Win|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFFFCC|Tie|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFCCCC|Loss|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n\n{{football box collapsible\n|round = 1\n|date = 2007-01-28\n|team1 = [[Club Deportivo Universidad Cat\u00f3lica|Universidad Cat\u00f3lica]] \n|score = 1 \u2013 0\n|report= \n|team2 = [[Santiago Wanderers]] \n|goals1 = [[Luis N\u00fa\u00f1ez (Chilean footballer)|N\u00fa\u00f1ez]] {{goal|83}}\n|goals2 = \n|stadium = [[Estadio San Carlos de Apoquindo|San Carlos de Apoquindo]]\n|location = [[Santiago, Chile|Santiago]]\n|attendance = 4.474 espectators\n|referee = [[Jorge Osorio]]\n|result=L\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round = 2\n|date = 2007-02-03\n|team1 = [[CD O'Higgins]] \n|score = 3 \u2013 2\n|report= \n|team2 = [[Santiago Wanderers]] \n|goals1 = [[Nicol\u00e1s Diez|Diez]] {{goal|7}} <br> [[Miguel Aceval|Aceval]] {{goal|39|pk}} <br> [[Adri\u00e1n Rojas|Rojas]] {{goal|78}}\n|goals2 = [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Jim\u00e9nez|Jim\u00e9nez]] {{goal|24|pk}} <br> [[Eric Godoy|Godoy]] {{goal|30}}\n|stadium = [[Estadio El Teniente]]\n|location = [[Rancagua]]\n|attendance = \n|referee =