 drummer, Lucas Fox, leaves the band. He is replaced by Phil \"Philthy Animal\" Taylor.\n* [[Ritchie Blackmore]] leaves Deep Purple, and is replaced by ex-[[James Gang]] guitarist [[Tommy Bolin]].\n\n==1976==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Black Flag (band)|Black Flag]]\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]/Vow Wow\n* [[Diamond Head (English band)|Diamond Head]]\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]\n* [[Ratt]]\n* [[Rose Tattoo]]\n* [[Running Wild (band)|Running Wild]]\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]\n* [[Billy Idol]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Argent (band)|Argent]]\n* [[Deep Purple]]\n* [[Montrose (band)|Montrose]]\n* [[Steppenwolf (band)|Steppenwolf]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[High Voltage (1976 album)|High Voltage]]''\n* AC/DC&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap]]'' AUS #4\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rocks (Aerosmith album)|Rocks]]'' US #3\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alice Cooper Goes to Hell]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Whole World's Goin' Crazy]]''\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Flyin' High (album)|Flyin' High]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Technical Ecstasy]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Agents of Fortune]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Bow Wow''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[If I Were Brittania I'd Waive the Rules]]''\n* [[Buffalo (band)|Buffalo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mother's Choice]]''\n* [[Grand Funk Railroad]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Born to Die (Grand Funk Railroad album)|Born to Die]]''\n* Grand Funk Railroad&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Good Singin', Good Playin']]''\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dreamboat Annie]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]- ''[[Sad Wings of Destiny]]''\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Destroyer (Kiss album)|Destroyer]]''\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rock and Roll Over]]''\n* [[Led Zeppelin]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Presence (album)|Presence]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Montrose (band)|Montrose]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Jump on It (Montrose album)|Jump on It]]''\n* [[Queen (band)|Queen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[A Day at the Races (album)|A Day At The Races]]'' The Billboard 200 #5<ref name=\"AllMusic\">AllMusic</ref>\n* [[Rainbow (English band)|Rainbow]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rising (Rainbow album)|Rising]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[2112 (album)|2112]]'' CAN #5\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Virgin Killer]]''\n* [[Slade]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nobody's Fools]]''\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Free-for-All (Ted Nugent album)|Free-for-All]]''\n* [[The Runaways]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Runaways (album)|The Runaways]]''\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Jailbreak (album)|Jailbreak]]'' UK #10\n* Thin Lizzy&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Johnny the Fox]]''\n*[[Truth and Janey]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''No Rest For The Wicked''\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No Heavy Petting]]''\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[High and Mighty (album)|High and Mighty]]''\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[New England (Wishbone Ash album)|New England]]''\n* [[Y&T]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Yesterday & Today (Y&T album)|Yesterday & Today]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Led Zeppelin]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Song Remains the Same (album)|The Song Remains the Same]]'' US #2 UK #1\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[All the World's a Stage (album)|All the World's a Stage]]'' CAN #6\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap (song)|Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap]]\"\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dream On (Aerosmith song)|Dream On]]\" US #6 (re-issue)\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Back in the Saddle]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Last Child]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Rats in the Cellar]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Walk This Way]]\" US #10 (re-issue)\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[(Don't Fear) The Reaper]]\"\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Magic Man]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Crazy on You]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dreamboat Annie (song)|Dreamboat Annie]]\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;