too album)|Rose Tattoo]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hemispheres (1978 album)|Hemispheres]]''\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Weekend Warriors (album)|Weekend Warriors]]''\n* [[The Runaways]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[And Now... The Runaways]]''\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Obsession (UFO album)|Obsession]]''\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fallen Angel (Uriah Heep album)|Fallen Angel]]''\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Van Halen (album)|Van Halen]]''\n* [[The Who]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Who Are You]]''\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;- ''[[Trouble (Whitesnake album)|Trouble]]''\n* [[Y&T]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Struck Down]]''\n* [[Yes (band)|Yes]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tormato]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[If You Want Blood You've Got It]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Some Enchanted Evening]]''\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tokyo Tapes (album)|Tokyo Tapes]]''(Europe)\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Double Live Gonzo]]''\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live and Dangerous]]'' UK #2\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Riff Raff\"\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Rock 'n' Roll Damnation]]\"\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Never Say Die (Black Sabbath song)|Never Say Die]]\"\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Heartless (Heart song)|Heartless]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Straight On]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dog & Butterfly (song)|Dog & Butterfly]]\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Better By You, Better Than Me]]\"\n* Judas Priest&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Beyond the Realms of Death (song)|Beyond the Realms of Death]]\"\n* Judas Priest&nbsp;\u2013 \"Stained Class\"\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Only You Can Rock Me\"\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Ain't Talkin' 'bout Love]]\"\n* Van Halen&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Eruption (instrumental)|Eruption]]/[[You Really Got Me#Van Halen version|You Really Got Me]]\"\n* Van Halen&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Jamie's Cryin']]\"\n* Van Halen&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Runnin' with the Devil]]\"\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[No Smoke Without Fire]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Brian Robertson (guitarist)|Brian Robertson]] exits Thin Lizzy, Gary Moore rejoins in his place.\n* [[Def Leppard]]'s drummer [[Rick Allen (drummer)|Rick Allen]] joins at 15 as a permanent member.\n* [[The Who]]'s drummer [[Keith Moon]] dies of a Clomethiazole overdose on September 6, he was 32.\n* Scorpions' desire to move to a more commercial type of metal sound causes Ulrich Roth to leave for a solo career. He is replaced with [[Matthias Jabs]].\n\n==1979==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]]\n* [[Gamma (band)|Gamma]]\n* [[TSA (band)|TSA]]\n* [[Kat (band)|KAT]]\n* [[Michael Schenker Group]]\n* [[Picture (band)|Picture]]\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]\n* [[Witchfinder General (band)|Witchfinder General]]\n* [[Hanoi Rocks]]\n* [[V8 (band)|V8]]\n* [[Salem (UK band)|Salem (UK)]]\n* [[Satan (band)|Satan]]\n* [[Boss (band) |Boss]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Blue Cheer]] (Second hiatus)\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Highway to Hell]]'' UK #8\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Accept (Accept album)|Accept]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Night in the Ruts]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Harder ... Faster]]''\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Strikes (album)|Strikes]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mirrors (Blue \u00d6yster Cult album)|Mirrors]]''\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]&nbsp;- ''[[Head Games (album)|Head Games]]''\n* [[Gamma (band)|Gamma]]&nbsp;- ''[[Gamma 1]]''\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;- ''[[Mr. Universe (album)|Mr. Universe]]''\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dynasty (Kiss album)|Dynasty]]'' US #9 (Disco single \"I Was Made for Loving You\" led to accusations of sellout, band's popularity suffered for several years)\n* [[Led Zeppelin]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[In Through the Out Door]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Magnum (band)|Magnum]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[