album)|Invasion]]''\n* [[Michael Schenker Group]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Michael Schenker Group (album)|The Michael Schenker Group]]'' UK #8\n* [[Molly Hatchet]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Beatin' the Odds (Molly Hatchet album)|Beatin' the Odds]]''\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ace of Spades (album)|Ace of Spades]]'' UK #4\n* [[Nazareth (band)|Nazareth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Malice in Wonderland (Nazareth album)|Malice in Wonderland]]\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blizzard of Ozz]]'' UK #7\n* [[Phil Lynott]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Solo in Soho]]'' UK #28\n* [[Quartz_(British_band)|Quartz]]&nbsp;- ''Stand Up and Fight''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Permanent Waves]]'' UK #3\n* [[Sammy Hagar]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Danger Zone (Sammy Hagar album)|Danger Zone]]'' UK #25\n* [[Samson (band)|Samson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Head On (Samson album)|Head On]]'' UK #34\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wheels of Steel]]'' UK #5\n* Saxon&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Strong Arm of the Law]]'' UK#11\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Animal Magnetism (Scorpions album)|Animal Magnetism]]'' UK #23\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Just Supposin']]'' UK #4\n* [[Styx (band)|Styx]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Paradise Theatre (album)|Paradise Theater]]'' UK #8\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Scream Dream]]'' UK #37\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Chinatown (Thin Lizzy album)|Chinatown]]'' UK #7\n* [[Triumph (band)|Triumph]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Progressions of Power]]'' UK #63\n* [[Trust (French band)|Trust ]]&nbsp;\u2013 '[[R\u00e9pression]]'\n* [[Tygers of Pan Tang]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wild Cat (Tygers of Pan Tang album)|Wild Cat]]'' UK #18\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No Place to Run]]'' UK #11\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Conquest (Uriah Heep album)|Conquest]]'' UK #37\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013''[[Women and Children First]]'' UK #15\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ready an' Willing]]'' UK #6\n* [[Wild Horses (British band)|Wild Horses]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wild Horses (Wild Horses album)|Wild Horses]]'' UK #38\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Just Testing]]''\n* [[Witchfynde]]&nbsp; - '[[Give 'Em Hell (Witchfynde album)|Give 'Em Hell]]'\n* [[Yes (band)|Yes]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Drama (Yes album)|Drama]]''\n\n===Compilation albums===\n* ''Killer Watts'' UK #27\n* ''[[Metal for Muthas|Metal for Muthas Volume 1]]'' UK #16\n* ''[[Metal for Muthas|Metal for Muthas Volume 2]]'' UK #58\n* ''Axe Attack Volume 1'' UK #15\n* ''Monsters of Rock'' UK #16\n* ''Precious Metal'' UK #60\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live at Last (Black Sabbath album)|Live at Last]]'' UK #5   (originally recorded in 1973)\n* [[Vardis]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''100 mph Live'' UK #52\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live...in the Heart of the City]]'' UK #5\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Rock and Roll Ain't Noise Pollution]]\" UK #15\n* AC/DC&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[You Shook Me All Night Long]]\" UK #38\n* [[Angel Witch]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Sweet Danger\" UK #75\n* Black Sabbath&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Neon Knights]]\" UK #22\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Die Young (Black Sabbath song)|Die Young]]\" UK #41\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Heaven and Hell (Black Sabbath song)|Heaven and Hell]]\"\n* [[Def Leppard]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Hello America (song)|Hello America]]\" UK #45\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Sleeping on the Job]]\"  UK #55\n* [[Iron Maiden]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Running Free]]\" UK #34\n* Iron Maiden&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Sanctuary (Iron Maiden song)|Sanctuary]]\" UK #29\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Breaking the Law]]\" UK #12\n* Judas Priest&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Living After Midnight]]\" UK #12\n* Judas Priest&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[United (Judas Priest song)|United]]\" UK #26\n* [[Michael Schenker Group]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Armed and Ready]]\" UK #53\n* Michael Schenker Group&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cry for the Nations]]\" UK #56\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Ace of Spades (song)|Ace of Spades]]\" UK #15\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Crazy Train]]\" UK #49\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mr Crowley]]\" UK #46\n* [[Phil Lynott]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dear Miss Lonely Hearts]]\" UK #32\n* Phil Lynott&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[King's Call]]\" UK #35\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Spirit of Radio]]\" UK #13\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Wheels of Steel\" UK #20\n* Saxon&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[747 (Strangers in the Night)]]\" UK #13\n* Saxon&nbsp;\u2013 \"Strong Arm of the Law\" UK #63\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Make It Real\" UK #72\n* Scorpions&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Zoo (Scorpions song)|The Zoo]]\" UK #75\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[What You're Proposing]]\" UK #2\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Lies (Status Quo song)|Lies]]\" UK #11\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Killer on the Loose]]\" UK #10\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Chinatown\" UK #21\n* [[Triumph (band)|Triumph]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[I Live for the Weekend]]\" UK #59\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Young Blood\" UK #36\n* [[Vardis]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Let's Go\" UK #59\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Ready an' Willing\" UK #43\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Fool for Your Loving]]\" UK #13\n\n===Events===\n* [[Bon Scott]], lead singer of [[AC/DC]], dies at 33 on February 19 after a binge of heavy drinking.\n* [[John Bonham]], drummer for [[Led Zeppelin]], dies at 32 on September 25, after a binge of heavy drinking. His death was similar to [[Bon Scott]]'s, and caused [[Led Zeppelin]] to disband.\n* ''[[Metal for Muthas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[New wave of British heavy metal]] compilation albums are released. ''Volume One'' reaches UK #16 and features the likes of Iron Maiden, Sledgehammer, EF Band, Toad The Wet Sprocket, Praying Mantis, Ethel The Frog, Angel Witch, Samson and Nutz, whilst, ''Volume Two'' reaches UK #58 and features the likes of Trespass, Eazy Money, Xero, White Spirit, Dark Star, Horsepower, Red Alert, Chevy and The Raid.\n* Metal for Muthas Tour, featuring Iron Maiden, Samson and Angel Witch becomes a resounding success, thanks to fan support and rave reviews from music press journalists.\n* Rainbow headlines the initial [[Monsters of Rock|Donington Festival]] 16 August 1980. Judas Priest, Scorpions, April Wine, Saxon, Riot, and Touch also play.  35,000 fans attend the event.\n* April 1: [[Brian Johnson]] joins AC/DC replacing Bon Scott as lead singer.\n* [[Mike Varney]] founds [[Shrapnel Records]].\n* Iron Maiden lead guitarist Dennis Stratton leaves and is replaced by [[Adrian Smith]].\n* Former [[Pink Floyd]] guitarist [[Snowy White]] joins Thin Lizzy.\n\n==1981==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]\n* [[Dark Angel (band)|Dark Angel]]\n* [[Icon (band)|Icon]]\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]\n* [[Mercyful Fate]]\n* [[Metallica]]\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]\n* [[Pantera]]\n* [[Show-Ya]]\n* [[Slayer]]\n* [[Sodom (band)|Sodom]]\n* [[Tarantula (band)|Tarantula]]\n* [[Vandenberg (band)|Vandenberg]]\n* [[Tokyo Blade]]\n\n===Albums===\nAlbum Chart Information courtesy of the book ''[[Guinness Hits Of The 80s]]''\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Breaker (Accept album)|Breaker]]''\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[For Those About to Rock We Salute You]]'' UK #3\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Special Forces (Alice Cooper album)|Special Forces]]'' UK #98\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]&nbsp;- ''[[Hard 'n' Heavy]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Nature of the Beast (album)|The Nature of the Beast]]'' UK #48\n* [[Bernie Marsden]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Look at Me Now (Bernie Marsden album)|Look At Me Now]]'' UK #71\n* [[Black Flag (band)|Black Flag]]&nbsp;- ''[[Damaged (Black Flag album)|Damaged]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mob Rules (album)|Mob Rules]]'' UK #12\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Marauder (Blackfoot album)|Marauder]]'' UK #38\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fire of Unknown Origin]]'' UK #29\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Hard Dog''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nightflight (Budgie album)|Nightflight]]'' UK #68\n* [[Cozy Powell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tilt (Cozy Powell album)|Tilt]]'' UK #58\n* [[Def Leppard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[High 'n' Dry]]'' UK #26\n* [[Dokken]]&nbsp;- ''[[Breaking the Chains (album)|Breaking the Chains]]''\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[4 (Foreigner album)|4]]'' UK #5\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dirty Fingers]]''\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;- ''[[Double Trouble (Gillan album)|Double Trouble]]''\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Future Shock (Gillan album)|Future Shock]]'' UK #2\n* [[Girlschool]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hit and Run (Girlschool album)|Hit and Run]]'' UK #5\n* [[Graham Bonnet]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Line-Up (Graham Bonnet album)|Line Up]]'' UK #62\n* [[Grand Funk Railroad]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Grand Funk Lives]]''\n* [[Hanoi Rocks]]&nbsp;- ''[[Bangkok Shocks, Saigon Shakes, Hanoi Rocks]]''\n* [[Humble Pie (band)|Humble Pie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Go for the Throat]]''\n* [[Iron Maiden]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Killers (Iron Maiden album)|Killers]]'' UK #12\n* [[Jim Steinman]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bad for Good]]'' UK #7\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Point of Entry]]'' UK #14\n* [[King Crimson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Discipline (King Crimson album)|Discipline]]''\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Music from \"The Elder\"|The Elder]] UK #51\n* [[Krokus (band)|Krokus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hardware (album)|Hardware]] UK #44\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Birthday Eve]]''\n* [[Meat Loaf]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dead Ringer (album)|Dead Ringer]]'' UK #1\n* [[Michael Schenker Group]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[MSG (album)|MSG]]'' UK #14\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Too Fast For Love]]''\n* [[Nazareth (band)|Nazareth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Fool Circle]]'' UK #60\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Diary of a Madman (album)|Diary of a Madman]]'' UK #14\n* [[Pat Benatar]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Precious Time (album)