ass]]\n* Majesty/[[Dream Theater]]\n* [[Gogmagog (band)|Gogmagog]]\n* [[Guns N' Roses]]\n* [[Iced Earth]]\n* [[King Diamond (band)|King Diamond]]\n* [[Macabre (band)|Macabre]]\n* [[Mr. Bungle]]\n* [[Neurosis (band)|Neurosis]]\n* [[Slave Raider]]\n* [[Stone Temple Pilots]]\n* [[Stormtroopers of Death]] (S.O.D.)\n* [[White Zombie (band)|White Zombie]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Mercyful Fate]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fly on the Wall (AC/DC album)|Fly on the Wall]]'' UK #7 AUS #4\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Metal Heart]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Done With Mirrors]]'', original lineup reunites\n* [[Alcatrazz]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Disturbing the Peace (album)|Disturbing the Peace]]'', with Steve Vai\n* [[Angel Witch]]&nbsp;- ''[[Screamin' 'n' Bleedin']]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Spreading the Disease]]''\n* [[Armored Saint]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Delirious Nomad]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Return......]]''\n* [[Black Flag (band)|Black Flag]]&nbsp;\u2013 '' [[Loose Nut]], [[In My Head (album)|In My Head]]''\n* [[Blitzkrieg (heavy metal band)|Blitzkrieg]]&nbsp;- ''[[A Time of Changes (album)|A Time of Changes]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Club Ninja]]''\n* [[Bon Jovi]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[7800\u00b0 Fahrenheit]]''\n* [[Celtic Frost]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[To Mega Therion (album)|To Mega Therion]]''\n* [[The Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Love (Cult album)|Love]]'' UK #4\n* [[Dark Angel (band)|Dark Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[We Have Arrived (album)|We Have Arrived]]''\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sacred Heart (Dio album)|Sacred Heart]]'' UK #4\n* [[Dokken]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Under Lock and Key]]''\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]]&nbsp;- ''[[Long Live the Loud]]''\n* [[Exodus (band)|Exodus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bonded by Blood]]''\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]]&nbsp;- ''[[Waiting for the Roar]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Spectre Within]]''\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[R