er]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hell Awaits]]''\n* [[Tokyo Blade]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Black Hearts & Jaded Spades]]''\n* [[Turbo (Polish band)|Turbo]]&nbsp;- ''[[Smak Ciszy]]''\n* [[Twisted Sister]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Come Out and Play (Twisted Sister album)|Come Out and Play]]''\n* [[Tygers of Pan Tang]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Wreck-Age]]''\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Misdemeanor (UFO album)|Misdemeanor]]''\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Equator (Uriah Heep album)|Equator]]''\n* [[V8 (Argentine band)|V8]]&nbsp;- ''Un Paso Mas En La Batalla''\n* [[Vandenberg (band)|Vandenberg]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alibi (Vandenberg album)|Alibi]]''\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[Possessed (Venom album)|Possessed]]''\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]&nbsp;- ''[[Soldiers of the Night]]''\n* [[Voivod (band)|Voivod]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rrr\u00f6\u00f6\u00f6aaarrr]]''\n* [[W.A.S.P. (band)|W.A.S.P.]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Last Command (album)|The Last Command]]\"\n* [[Warlock (band)|Warlock]]&nbsp;- ''[[Hellbound (Warlock album)|Hellbound]]''\n* [[Watchtower (band)|Watchtower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Energetic Disassembly]]''\n* [[Waysted]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Good the Bad the Waysted]]''\n* [[White Lion]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fight to Survive]]''\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Raw to the Bone]]''\n* [[Yngwie J. Malmsteen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Marching Out]]''\n* [[Y&T]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Down for the Count (album)|Down for the Count]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Iron Maiden]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live After Death]]'' UK #2\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[World Wide Live]]'' GER #4\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Armed and Dangerous\"\n* Anthrax&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Madhouse (song)|Madhouse]]\"\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[What About Love|What About Love?]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Never (Heart song)|Never]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[These Dreams]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Nothin' at All (Heart song)|Nothin' At All]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[If