art&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[I Want You So Bad]]\"\n* [[Helloween]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"A Tale That Wasn't Right\"\n* Helloween&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Future World (Helloween song)|Future World]]\"\n* Helloween&nbsp;\u2013 \"Halloween\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Parental Guidance (Judas Priest song)|Parental Guidance]]\"\n* [[Kreator]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Behind the Mirror (song)|Behind the Mirror]]\"\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Girls, Girls, Girls (M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce song)|Girls, Girls, Girls]]\"\n* M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Wild Side (M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce song)|Wild Side]]\"\n* M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[You're All I Need (song)|You're All I Need]]\"\n* [[Savatage]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Hall of the Mountain King\"\n* Savatage&nbsp;\u2013 \"24 Hours Ago\"\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Possessed to Skate\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"War Inside My Head\"\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Over the Wall\"\n* [[Warlock (band)|Warlock]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[All We Are]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Bon Jovi]] headlines the [[Monsters of Rock]] festival at Donington, England on a bill which includes [[Dio (band)|Dio]], [[Metallica]], [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]], [[W.A.S.P. (band)|W.A.S.P.]] and [[Cinderella (band)|Cinderella]].\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]'s drummer Pete Gill leaves the band and Phil Taylor returns.\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Girls, Girls, Girls (M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce album)|Girls, Girls, Girls]]'' debuts at #5 on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]] chart.\n* [[Guns N' Roses]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Appetite for Destruction]]'' goes on to become the best selling debut album of all time with over 28 million copies sold to date.\n\n==1988==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Acheron (band)|Acheron]]\n* [[Badlands (American band)|Badlands]]\n* [[The Big F]]\n* [[Biohazard (band)|Biohazard]]\n* [[Buckethead]]\n* [[B'z]]\n* [[Cadaver (band)|Cadaver]]\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]\n* [[Carnage (band)|Carnage]]\n* [[Cryptopsy]]\n* [[Deftones]]\n* [[Dismember (band)|Dismember]]\n* [[Electric Boys]]\n* [[Gorefest]]\n* [[Herm\u00e9tica]]\n* [[Mr. Big (band)|Mr. Big]]\n* [[Nine Inch Nails]]\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]\n* [[Saigon Kick]]\n* [[Soziedad Alkoholika]]\n* [[The Almighty (band)|The Almighty]]\n* [[Tiamat (band)|Tiamat]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Warlock (band)|Warlock]]\n* [[V8 (band)|V8]]\n* [[Vanilla Fudge]] (Third hiatus)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blow Up Your Video]]'' UK #2 AUS #2\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[State of Euphoria]]''\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Pound for Pound]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blood Fire Death]]''\n* [[Jason Becker]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Perpetual Burn]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Battalions of Fear]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Imaginos]]''\n* [[Bolt Thrower (band)|Bolt Thrower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[In Battle There Is No Law]]''\n* [[Bon Jovi]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[New Jersey (album)|New Jersey]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Cinderella (band)|Cinderella]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Long Cold Winter]]'' US #10\n* [[David Lee Roth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Skyscraper (album)|Skyscraper]]'' US #6\n* [[Danzig (band)|Danzig]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Danzig (album)|Danzig]]''\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Leprosy (album)|Leprosy]]''\n* [[Death Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Frolic through the Park]]''\n* [[Dokken]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Beast from the East]]''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]]&nbsp;- ''[[Out of This World (Europe album)|Out of This World]]''\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]]&nbsp;- ''[[Exciter (O.T.T.)]]''\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]]&nbsp;- ''[[On Target]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]]&nbsp;- ''[[No Exit (Fates Warning album)|No Exit]]''\n* [[Flotsam and Jetsam (band)|Flotsam and Jetsam]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No Place for Disgrace]]''\n* [[Girlschool]]&nbsp;- ''[[Take a Bite]]''\n* [[Guns N' Roses]]&nbsp;\u2013