wn (song)|Ram It Down]]\"\n* [[Living Colour]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cult of Personality]]\"\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[In My Darkest Hour]]\"\n* Megadeth&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Liar (Megadeth song)|Liar]]\"\n* Megadeth&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mary Jane (Megadeth song)|Mary Jane]]\"\n* [[Metallica]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[One (Metallica song)|One]]\"\n* Metallica&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Harvester of Sorrow]]\"\n* Metallica&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Shortest Straw\"\n* Metallica&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dyers Eve]]\"\n* Metallica&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Blackened (song)|Blackened]]\"\n* Queensr\u00ffche&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Eyes of a Stranger (song)|Eyes of a Stranger]]\"\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Dissident Aggressor\"\n* Slayer&nbsp;\u2013 \"Mandatory Suicide\"\n* Slayer&nbsp;\u2013 \"South of Heaven\"\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Pledge Your Allegiance\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"Surf and Slam\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Trip at the Brain]]\"\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Trial by Fire\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Iron Maiden]] headlines the [[Monsters of Rock]] festival at Donington, England to the largest crowd in the venue's history (107,000),<ref name=\"Wall269\">{{cite book | author=Wall, Mick | title=Iron Maiden: Run to the Hills, the Authorised Biography (3rd ed.)| publisher=Sanctuary Publishing | year=2004 | isbn=1-86074-542-3 |page=269}}</ref> on a bill which includes [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]], [[David Lee Roth]], [[Megadeth]], [[Guns n' Roses]] and [[Helloween]]. Two fans were accidentally crushed to death during Guns N' Roses performance of \"[[It's So Easy (Guns N' Roses song)|It's So Easy]]\".\n* Bon Jovi's album ''[[New Jersey (album)|New Jersey]]'' sets the record for the hard rock album to spawn the most Top 10 singles, with five singles charting on the Top 10 of the Billboard Hot 100 Singles Chart in United States\n* Metallica's ''[[...And Justice for All (album)|...And Justice for All]]'' receives a [[Grammy Award]] nomination for Best Metal Performance, but lose to the non-metal act [[Jethro Tull (band)|Jethro Tull]].\n\n==1989==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]\n* [[The Black Crowes]]\n* [[Comecon (band)|Comecon]]\n* [[Dark Tranquillity]]\n* [[Doro (musician)|Doro]] (former [[Warlock (band)|Warlock]] singer)\n* [[Dungeon (band)|Dungeon]]\n* [[Edge of Sanity]]\n* [[Gamma ray (band)|Gamma Ray]]\n* [[Living Sacrifice]]\n* [[Luna Sea]]\n* [[Marilyn Manson (band)|Marilyn Manson]]\n* [[Novembers Doom]]\n* [[Platero y T\u00fa]]\n* [[Sentenced]]\n* [[Slaughter (band)|Slaughter]]\n* [[The Gathering (band)|The Gathering]]\n* [[Therapy?]]\n* [[The Wildhearts]]\n* [[Type O Negative]]\n* [[Ugly Kid Joe]]\n* [[Unanimated]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Cacophony (band)|Cacophony]]\n* [[Dokken]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Eat the Heat]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Pump]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Trash (Alice Cooper album)|Trash]]'' UK #2\n* [[Autopsy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Severed Survival]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wild Obsession]]''\n* [[The Big F]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''The Big F''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Headless Cross (album)|Headless Cross]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Follow the Blind]]''\n* [[Blue Murder (band)|Blue Murder]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blue Murder (album)|Blue Murder]]''\n* [[Bolt Thrower (band)|Bolt Thrower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Realm of Chaos (album)|Realm Of Chaos]]''\n* [[The Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sonic Temple]]'' US #10 UK #3\n* [[Dark Angel (band)|Dark Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Leave Scars]]''\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[When Dream and Day Unite]]''\n* [[Exodus (band)|Exodus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fabulous Disaster]]''\n* [[Extreme (band)|Extreme]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Extreme (album)|Extreme]]\n* [[Faith No More]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Real Thing (Faith No More album)|The Real Thing]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]]&nbsp;- ''[[Perfect Symmetry (Fates Warning album)|Perfect Symmetry]]''\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Aft