 to excessive touring and musical differences and replaced by [[Roland Grapow]].  A short while after, Hansen announced that he was starting his own group, called [[Gamma Ray (band)|Gamma Ray]].\n* [[Bon Jovi]] headlined an outdoor concert at [[Milton Keynes Bowl]] which saw support from [[Europe (band)|Europe]], [[Skid Row (American band)|Skid Row]] and [[Vixen (band)|Vixen]].\n\n==1990==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Allegiance (Australian band)|Allegiance]]\n* [[Amorphis]]\n* [[Anathema (band)|Anathema]]\n* [[At the Gates]]\n* [[Body Count (band)|Body Count]]\n* [[Clutch (band)|Clutch]]\n* [[Converge (band)|Converge]]\n* [[Fear Factory]]\n* [[Hypocrisy (band)|Hypocrisy]]\n* [[In Flames]]\n* [[Infectious Grooves]]\n* [[Krisiun]]\n* [[Kyuss]]\n* [[Lacrimosa_(band)|Lacrimosa]]\n* [[Monstrosity (band)|Monstrosity]]\n* [[Opeth]]\n* [[Pearl Jam]]\n* [[Septic Flesh|SepticFlesh]]\n* [[Tool (band)|Tool]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Icon (band)|Icon]]\n* [[Quiet Riot]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Praying Mantis (band)|Praying Mantis]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Razors Edge (AC/DC album)|The Razors Edge]]'' US #2 UK #4 AUS #3\n* [[Alice in Chains]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Facelift (album)|Facelift]]''\n* [[Annihilator (band)|Annihilator]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Never, Neverland]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Persistence of Time]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hammerheart]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tyr (album)|Tyr]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tales from the Twilight World]]''\n* [[Blue Cheer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Highlights and Lowlives]]''\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tattooed Millionaire]]''\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Eaten Back to Life]]''\n* [[Cinderella (band)|Cinderella]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Heartbreak Station]]''\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Spiritual Healing (album)|Spiritual Healing]]''\n* [[Death Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Act III (Death Angel album)|Act I