 Wanted]]''\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Waste Lands (album)|The Waste Lands]]''\n* [[W.A.S.P. (band)|W.A.S.P.]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[The Crimson Idol]]\n* [[White Zombie (band)|White Zombie]]&nbsp;\u2013 '' [[La Sexorcisto: Devil Music, Vol. 1]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[AC/DC Live|Live]]'' UK #5 AUS #1\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Lights Out in Tokyo Live''\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Pull Me Under]]\"\n* [[Exodus (American band)|Exodus]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Thorn in My Side\"\n* [[Faith No More]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Midlife Crisis]]\"\n* [[Iron Maiden]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Afraid to Shoot Strangers\"\n* Iron Maiden&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Be Quick or Be Dead]]\" UK #2\n* Iron Maiden&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[From Here to Eternity (Iron Maiden song)|From Here to Eternity]]\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Night Crawler\"\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"God Gave Rock N' Roll to You II\"\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Symphony Of Destruction]]\"\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Foreclosure of a Dream]]\"\n* Megadeth&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Skin o' My Teeth]]\"\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Come as You Are (Nirvana song)|Come As You Are]]\" US #3\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Lithium (Nirvana song)|Lithium]]\"\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[In Bloom]]\" US #5\n* [[Pearl Jam]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Even Flow]]\" US #3\n* [[Pearl Jam]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Jeremy (song)|Jeremy]]\" US #5\n* [[Rage Against the Machine]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Killing in the Name]]\"\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Asleep at the Wheel\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"I'll Hate You Better\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"Monopoly on Sorrow\"\n* Suicidal Tendencies&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Nobody Hears]]\"\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Electric Crown\"\n* Testament&nbsp;\u2013 \"Return to Serenity\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]'s drummer Phil Taylor finally leaves after recording \"Ain't No Nice Guy\" for the ''[[March \u00f6r Die]]'' album. The drummer on that album is Tommy Aldridge, who was replaced by Mikkey Dee after recording the album.\n* In April, [[The Freddie Mercury Tribute Concert]] is held. Top heavy metal acts such as [[Metallica]], [[Guns N' Roses]], [[Def Leppard]], [[Extreme (band)|Extreme]] and the heavy metal parody band [[Spinal Tap (band)|Spinal Tap]] perform, as well as heavy metal/hard rock legends such as [[Robert Plant]] ([[Led Zeppelin]]), [[Tony Iommi]] ([[Black Sabbath]]) and [[Roger Daltrey]] ([[The Who]]).\n* [[Iron Maiden]] headlines the [[Monsters of Rock]] festival at Donington, England on a bill which includes [[Skid Row (American band)|Skid Row]], [[Thunder (band)|Thunder]], [[Slayer]], [[W.A.S.P. (band)|W.A.S.P.]] and [[The Almighty (band)|The Almighty]].\n\n==1993==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Apocalyptica]]\n* [[Children of Bodom]]\n* [[Coal Chamber]]\n* [[Dark Funeral]]\n* [[Dimmu Borgir]]\n* [[Fight (band)|Fight]]\n* [[Fury (Australian band)|Fury]]\n* [[HammerFall]]\n* [[Korn]]\n* [[Korpiklaani]]\n* [[Mournful Congregation]]\n* [[Mushroomhead]]\n* [[Nile (band)|Nile]]\n* [[Rhapsody of Fire]]\n* [[Sacrificium]]\n* [[Theatre of Tragedy]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Judas Priest]] (Hiatus)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Mercyful Fate]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Objection Overruled (album)|Objection Overruled]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Get a Grip]]''\n* [[Angels_Cry_(album)|Angra - Angels Cry]]\n* [[Annihilator (band)|Annihilator]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Set the World on Fire (Annihilator album)|Set the World on Fire]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sound of White Noise]]'' US #7\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Attitude (April Wine album)|Attitude]]''\n* [[At the Gates]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[With Fear I Kiss the Burning Darkness]]''\n* [[The Big F]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Is''\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hammer Smashed Face]]'' (EP)\n* [[Carcass (band)