eart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Will You Be There (In the Morning)]]\"\n* [[Iron Maiden]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Fear of the Dark (song)|Fear of the Dark (Live)]]\" UK #8\n* Iron Maiden&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Hallowed Be Thy Name|Hallowed Be Thy Name (Live)]]\" UK #9\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Sweating Bullets (song)|Sweating Bullets]]\n* Megadeth&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Symphony of Destruction]]\"\n* [[Savatage]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Edge of Thorns\"\n* Savatage&nbsp;\u2013 \"Sleep\"\n* [[Sodom (band)|Sodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Aber bitte mit Sahne]]\"\n* [[Stone Temple Pilots]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Sex Type Thing]]\"\n* [[Stone Temple Pilots]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Plush (song)|Plush]]\"\n* [[Stone Temple Pilots]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Wicked Garden]]\"\n* [[Stone Temple Pilots]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Creep (Stone Temple Pilots song)|Creep]]\"\n* [[Tool (band)|Tool]]&nbsp;- \"[[Sober (Tool song)|Sober]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Iron Maiden]] vocalist [[Bruce Dickinson]] leaves the band to pursue his solo career. He would be replaced the following year by [[Blaze Bayley]].\n* [[Dokken]] reforms and tours without a new album.\n* [[Helloween]] drummer [[Ingo Schwichtenberg]] was having difficulties coping with personal and career-related demands and asked for time off for an unspecified period, he was replaced by [[Uli Kusch]].\n* [[Rob Halford]] of [[Judas Priest]] leaves the band to start his own project [[Fight (band)|Fight]].\n* [[Aerosmith]] headlines the [[Monsters of Rock]] festival at Donington, England on a bill which includes [[Extreme (band)|Extreme]], [[Sepultura]], [[Pantera]], [[Therapy?]] and [[Pride and Glory (band)|Pride and Glory]].\n* [[Helloween]] vocalist [[Michael Kiske]] was fired from the band for personal reasons and musical differences, he was replaced by [[Andi Deris]].\n* [[Varg Vikernes]] kills [[Euronymous]] of [[Mayhem (band)|Mayhem]], which forces the end of the norwegian Black Metal Scene.\n\n==1994==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Abscess (band)|Abscess]]\n* [[Amen (American band)|Amen]]\n* [[Destr\u00f6yer 666]]\n* [[Eternal Tears of Sorrow]]\n* [[Foo Fighters]]\n* [[Glenn Tipton]]\n* [[Heavenly (French band)|Heavenly]]\n* [[Hoobastank]]\n* [[Lacuna Coil]]\n* [[Lamb of God (band)|Lamb of God]]\n* [[Rammstein]]\n* [[Sevendust]]\n* [[Slash's Snakepit]]\n* [[Strapping Young Lad]]\n* [[Static-X]]\n* [[Symphony X]]\n* [[System Of A Down]]\n* [[The Killer Barbies]]\n* [[Xandria]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Herm\u00e9tica]]\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Rainbow (English band)|Rainbow]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Death Row (album)|Death Row]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Last Temptation (Alice Cooper album)|The Last Temptation]]'' UK #6\n* [[Alice in Chains]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Jar of Flies]]'' EP US #1\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Frigate (album)|Frigate]]''\n* [[At the Gates]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Terminal Spirit Disease]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Between the Walls]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Requiem (Bathory album)|Requiem]]''\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[After the Reign (album)|After the Reign]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Cross Purposes]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Cult Classic]]''\n* [[Body Count (band)|Body Count]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Born Dead]]''\n* [[Bolt Thrower (band)|Bolt Thrower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[...For Victory]]''\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Balls to Picasso]]''\n* [[Bush (British band)|Bush]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Sixteen Stone]]\" US #4\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Bleeding (album)|The Bleeding]]''\n* [[Cinderella (band)|Cinderella]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Still Climbing (Cinderella album)|Still Climbing]]''\n* [[Cryptopsy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blasphemy Made Flesh]]''\n* [[The Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Cult (album)|The Cult]]''\n* [[Darkthrone]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Transilvanian Hunger]]''\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Awake (Dream Theater album)|Awake]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]]&nb