r [[Mayhem (band)|Mayhem]] guitarist [[Euronymous]]\n* [[Kurt Cobain]] dies at the age of 27 due to what was officially ruled a suicide by a self-inflicted shotgun wound to the head, breaking up [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]].\n\n==1995==\n\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[3rd Strike (band)|3rd Strike]]\n* [[After Forever]]\n* [[Agalloch]]\n* [[Almafuerte (band)|Almafuerte]]\n* [[Autumn (band)|Autumn]]\n* [[Ayreon]]\n* [[Buckcherry]]\n* [[Chevelle (band)|Chevelle]]\n* [[Ensiferum]]\n* [[Evanescence]]\n* [[Godsmack]]\n* [[Hibernus Mortis]]\n* [[Kittie]]\n* [[Limp Bizkit]]\n* [[Moonsorrow]]\n* Pumpjack\n* [[Slipknot (band)|Slipknot]]\n* [[Staind]]\n* Tricky Beans/Tricky Means/[[Sonata Arctica]]\n* [[Trapt]]\n* [[Vanishing Point (band)|Vanishing Point]]\n* Whispering Gallery\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[The Big F]]\n* [[The Cult]]\n* Groundswell/[[Three Days Grace]]\n* [[Kyuss]] (in October)\n* [[Living Colour]] (in January)\n* [[Metal Church]] (until 1998)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ballbreaker]]'' US #4 UK #6 AUS #1\n* [[Alice in Chains]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alice in Chains (album)|Alice in Chains]]'' US #1\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stomp 442]]''\n* [[At the Gates]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Slaughter of the Soul]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Octagon (Bathory album)|Octagon]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Forbidden (Black Sabbath album)|Forbidden]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Imaginations From the Other Side]]''\n* [[Blitzkrieg (heavy metal band)|Blitzkrieg]]&nbsp;- ''Unholy Trinity''\n* [[Bon Jovi]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[These Days (Bon Jovi album)|These Days]]'' US #9 UK #1\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Bow Wow #1''\n* [[Darkthrone]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Panzerfaust (album)|Panzerfaust]]''\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Symbolic (Death album)|Symbolic]]''\n* [[Deftones]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Adrenaline (album)|Adrenaline]]''\n* [[Dokken]]&nbsp;\