 Remains (band)|All That Remains]]\n* [[Anaal Nathrakh]]\n* [[Andrew WK]]\n* [[Atreyu (band)|Atreyu]]\n* [[Beseech]]\n* [[Black Label Society]]\n* [[Bobaflex]]\n* [[Bullet For My Valentine]]\n* [[Chimaira]]\n* [[Cog (band)|Cog]]\n* [[Cult of Luna]]\n* [[Demons and Wizards (band)|Demons and Wizards]]\n* [[Freedom Call]]\n* [[The Giraffes (Brooklyn band)|The Giraffes]]\n* [[Kult ov Azazel]]\n* [[Liquid Tension Experiment]]\n* [[Metalium]]\n* [[Mnemic]]\n* [[Origin (band)|Origin]]\n* [[Rebaelliun]]\n* [[T\u00fdr (band)|T\u00fdr]]\n* [[Unearth]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Faith No More]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Metal Church]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Amon Amarth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Once Sent from the Golden Hall]]''\n* [[Fireworks_(Angra_album)|Angra - Fireworks]]\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Volume 8: The Threat Is Real]]''\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Inquisition Symphony (album)|Inquisition Symphony]]''\n* [[Arch Enemy (band)|Arch Enemy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stigmata (Arch Enemy album)|Stigmata]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Oceans of Time (Axel Rudi Pell album)|Oceans of Time]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nightfall in Middle-Earth]]''\n* [[Blitzkrieg (heavy metal band)|Blitzkrieg]]&nbsp;- ''The Mist of Avalon''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Heaven Forbid]]''\n* [[Bolt Thrower (band)|Bolt Thrower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mercenary (album)|Mercenary]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Back''\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Chemical Wedding (Bruce Dickinson album)|The Chemical Wedding]]''\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Gallery of Suicide]]''\n* [[Cryptopsy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Whisper Supremacy]]''\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Sound of Perseverance]]''\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Abandon (album)|Abandon]]''\n* [[Edguy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Vain Glory Opera]]''\n* [[Fear Factory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Obsolete (album)|Obsolete]]''\n* [[Godsmack]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Godsma