ot (band)|Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Inishmore (album)|Inishmore]]''\n* [[Rob Zombie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hellbilly Deluxe]]'' US #5\n* [[Running Wild (band)|Running Wild]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Rivalry (album)|The Rivalry]]''\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Diabolus in Musica]]''\n* [[Soulfly]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Soulfly (album)|Soulfly]]''\n* [[Spineshank]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Strictly Diesel]]''\n* [[Stratovarius]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Destiny (Stratovarius album)|Destiny]]'' FIN #1\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Six the Hard Way]]'' (EP)\n* [[Symphony X]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Twilight in Olympus]]''\n* [[System of a Down]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[System of a Down (album)|System of a Down]]''\n* [[Tankard (band)|Tankard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Disco Destroyer]]''\n* [[Tarantula (band)|Tarantula]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Light Beyond the Dark''\n* [[Tokyo Blade]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Pumphouse (album)|Pumphouse]]''\n* [[Tokyo Blade]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Mr. Ice''\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sonic Origami]]''\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Van Halen III]]'' US #4\n* [[Vanilla Ice]]&nbsp;- ''[[Hard To Swallow]]''\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]&nbsp;- ''[[Cyberchrist]]''\n* [[Vision of Disorder]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Imprint (Vision of Disorder album)|Imprint]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Reunion (Black Sabbath album)|Reunion]]''\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Inferno: Last in Live]]''\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Once in a LIVEtime]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[['98 Live Meltdown]]''\n* [[Yngwie J. Malmsteen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Double Live!]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Different Stages (Rush album)|Different Stages]]''\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[BBC Sessions (Saxon album)|BBC Sessions / Live at Reading Festival '86]]'' Originally recorded in 1986\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mirror Mirror (Blind Guardian song)|Mirror Mirror]]\"\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Chemical Wedding (Bruce D