eplica\"\n* Sonata Arctica&nbsp;\u2013 \"Kingdom for a Heart\"\n* [[Staind]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Home (Staind song)|Home]]\"\n* Staind&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Just Go (Staind song)|Just Go]]\"\n* Staind&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mudshovel]]\"\n* [[Static-X]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Push It (Static-X song)|Push It]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* Vocalist [[Blaze Bayley]] is asked to leave [[Iron Maiden]], following which they are rejoined by [[Bruce Dickinson]] and guitarist [[Adrian Smith]], creating their current six-piece line up.\n* During Edguy's [[Theater of Salvation]] tour, Tobias Sammet began to write down his ideas for a metal opera recruiting well-known metal musicians like [[Michael Kiske]], [[Andre Matos]], [[Kai Hansen]], [[Rob Rock]], [[Timo Tolkki]], [[Markus Grosskopf]] and more.\n\n==2000==\n\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]\n* [[Between the Buried and Me]]\n* [[Byzantine (band)|Byzantine]]\n* [[Circus Maximus (Norwegian band)|Circus Maximus]]\n* [[Crashd\u00efet]]\n* [[The Darkness (band)|The Darkness]]\n* [[Deathstars]]\n* [[Halford (band)|Halford]]\n* [[Mastodon (band)|Mastodon]]\n* [[Nightrage]]\n* [[Otep]]\n* [[Revocation (band)|Revocation]]\n* [[Steel Panther]]\n* [[Sylosis]]\n* [[Thunderstone (band)|Thunderstone]]\n* [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]]\n* [[Visions of Atlantis]]\n* [[Wolfmother]]\n* [[Yellowcard]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Rage Against the Machine]]\n* [[Primus (band)|Primus]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[A Perfect Circle]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mer De Noms]]''\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stiff Upper Lip]]'' US #7 AUS #3\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Brutal Planet]]''\n* [[Anthem (band)|Anthem]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Heavy Metal Anthem]]''\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Cult]]''\n* [[Armored Saint]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Revelation (Armored Saint album)|Revelation]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Masquerade Ball]]''\n* [[Black Label Society]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stronger Than Death]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Beyond''\n* [[Ch