ong)|Headstrong]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Alice in Chains]] singer [[Layne Staley]] dies on April 5 at 34 from an overdose of heroin.\n* [[The Who]] bassist [[John Entwistle]] dies on June 27 at 57 from a cocaine-induced heart attack.\n* Ex&nbsp;\u2013 [[Freedom Call]] guitarist [[Sascha Gerstner]] enter [[Helloween]] after the dismissal of [[Roland Grapow]]\n\n==2003==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Battlecross]]\n* [[Crystal Viper]]\n* [[Deathgaze]]\n* [[Double Dragon (band)|Double Dragon]]\n* [[Leaves' Eyes]]\n* [[Lord (band)|Lord]]\n* [[Ne Obliviscaris (band)|Ne Obliviscaris]]\n* [[Nothing More]]\n* [[Parkway Drive]]\n* [[Powerwolf]]\n* [[Skeletonwitch]]\n* [[The Sword]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Coal Chamber]] (until 2011)\n* [[Five pointe o]]\n* [[Pantera]]\n* [[Segression]] (until 2009)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Fear Factory]]\n* [[Primus (band)|Primus]]\n* [[Judas Priest]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[A Perfect Circle]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Thirteenth Step]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Eyes of Alice Cooper]]''\n* [[Anaal Nathrakh]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[When Fire Rains Down from the Sky, Mankind Will Reap As It Has Sown]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[We've Come for You All]]''\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Reflections (Apocalyptica album)|Reflections]]''\n* [[Arch Enemy (band)|Arch Enemy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Anthems of Rebellion]]''\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Frail Words Collapse]]''\n* [[Avenged Sevenfold]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Waking the Fallen]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nordland II]]''\n* [[Between The Buried And Me]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Silent Circus]]''\n* [[Black Label Society]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Blessed Hellride]]''\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[15 Year Killing Spree]]''\n* [[Cryptopsy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[None So Live]]''\n* [[Children Of Bodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hate Crew Deathroll]]'' FIN #1\n* [[Chimaira]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Impossibility of Reason]]''\n* [[Cul