ken]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hell to Pay (Dokken album)|Hell to Pay]]''\n* [[DragonForce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sonic Firestorm]]''\n* [[Dream Evil]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Book of Heavy Metal]]''\n* [[Dungeon (band)|Dungeon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[One Step Beyond (Dungeon album)|One Step Beyond]]''\n* [[Edguy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hellfire Club (album)|Hellfire Club]]''\n* [[Ensiferum]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Iron (Ensiferum album)|Iron]]''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]]&nbsp;- ''[[Start from the Dark]]''\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]]&nbsp;- ''New Testament''\n* [[Exodus (band)|Exodus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tempo of the Damned]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]]&nbsp;- ''[[FWX]]''\n* [[Fear Factory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Archetype (Fear Factory album)|Archetype]]''\n* [[Finntroll]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nattf\u00f6dd]]''\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Power of the Blues]]''\n* [[Girlschool]]&nbsp;- ''[[Believe (Girlschool album)|Believe]]''\n* [[God Forbid]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Gone Forever]]''\n* [[Godsmack]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Other Side (Godsmack album)|The Other Side]]'' EP US #5\n* [[Grip Inc.]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Incorporated (Grip Inc. album)|Incorporated]]\"\n* [[Guns N' Roses]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Greatest Hits (Guns N' Roses album)|Greatest Hits]]'' US #3 UK #1\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Jupiters Darling]]''\n* [[Iced Earth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Glorious Burden]]''\n* [[Killswitch Engage]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The End of Heartache]]''\n* [[Korn]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Greatest Hits, Vol. 1 (Korn album)|Greatest Hits, Volume 1]]'' US #4\n* [[Lamb Of God (band)|Lamb Of God]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ashes of the Wake]]''\n* [[Lostprophets]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Start Something]]'' UK #4\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Terror (album)|Terror]]''\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Racing (album)|Racing]]''\n* [[Magnum (band)|Magnum]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Brand New Morning (Magnum album)|Brand New Morning]]''\n* [[Marilyn Manson (band)|Marilyn Manson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lest We Forget: The Best Of]]'' US #9 UK #4\n* 