]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Dungeon (band)|Dungeon]]\n* [[Living Sacrifice]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dirty Diamonds]]''\n* [[Alice in Chains]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Essential Alice in Chains]]''\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Apocalyptica]]''\n* [[Arch Enemy (band)|Arch Enemy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Doomsday Machine (album)|Doomsday Machine]]''\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Shadows Are Security]]''\n* [[Audioslave]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Out of Exile]]'' US #1 UK #5\n* [[Avenged Sevenfold]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[City of Evil]]''\n* [[Between The Buried And Me]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alaska (Between the Buried and Me album)|Alaska]]''\n* [[Black Label Society]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mafia (Black Label Society album)|Mafia]]''\n* [[Blitzkrieg (heavy metal band)|Blitzkrieg]]&nbsp;- ''Sins and Greed''\n* [[Bolt Thrower (band)|Bolt Thrower]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Those Once Loyal]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Era''\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tyranny of Souls]]''\n* [[Bullet for My Valentine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Poison]]''\n* [[Byzantine (band)|Byzantine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[...And They Shall Take Up Serpents]]''\n* [[Candlemass (band)|Candlemass]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Candlemass (album)|Candlemass]]''\n* [[Children of Bodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Are You Dead Yet?]]'' FIN #1\n* [[Chimaira]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Chimaira (album)|Chimaira]]''\n* [[Circus Maximus (Norwegian band)|Circus Maximus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The 1st Chapter (album)|The 1st Chapter]]''\n* [[Cog (band)|Cog]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The New Normal (album)|The New Normal]]''\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rapture of the Deep]]''\n* [[Deftones]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[B-Sides & Rarities (Deftones)|B-Sides & Rarities]]''\n* [[Demons and Wizards (band)|Demons and Wizards]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Touched by the Crimson King]]''\n* [[Despised Icon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Healing Process]]''\n* [[DevilDriver]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Fury of Our Maker's Hand]]''\n* [[Diamond Head (English band)|Diamond