ry]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rio Grande Blood]]''\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Kiss of Death (Mot\u00f6rhead album)|Kiss of Death]]''\n* [[Norther]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Till Death Unites Us]]''\n* [[Psycroptic]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Symbols of Failure]]''\n* [[Queensr\u00ffche]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Operation: Mindcrime II]]''\n* [[Quiet Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rehab (Quiet Riot album)|Rehab]]''\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Army of One (album)|Army of One]]''\n* [[Rhapsody of Fire]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Triumph or Agony]]''\n* [[Rob Zombie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Educated Horses]]'' US #5\n* [[Sadus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Out for Blood (Sadus album)|Out for Blood]]''\n* [[Samson (band)|Samson]]&nbsp;- ''P.S''\n* [[Joe Satriani]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Super Colossal]]''\n* [[Satyricon (band)|Satyricon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Now, Diabolical]]''\n* [[Sepultura]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dante XXI]]''\n* [[Sikth]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Death of a Dead Day]]\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Christ Illusion]]'' US #5\n* [[Sodom (band)|Sodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sodom (album)|Sodom]]''\n* [[Spawn of Possession]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Noctambulant''\n* [[Tankard (band)|Tankard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Beauty and the Beer]]''\n* [[The Sword]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Age of Winters]]''\n* [[Threat Signal]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Under Reprisal]]''\n* [[Tool (band)|Tool]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[10,000 Days (Tool album)|10,000 Days]]'' US #1 UK #4\n* [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Crusade (album)|The Crusade]]'' UK #7\n* [[Twisted Sister]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[A Twisted Christmas]]''\n* [[T\u00fdr (band)|T\u00fdr]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ragnarok (T\u00fdr album)|Ragnarok]]''\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Monkey Puzzle (UFO album)|The Monkey Puzzle]]''\n* [[Underoath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Define the Great Line]]'' US #2\n* [[Unearth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[III: In the Eyes of Fire]]''\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[Metal Black]]''\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]&nbsp;- ''[[Warball]]''\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Clan Destiny]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n*