d)|Magnum]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Princess Alice and the Broken Arrow]]''\n* [[Manowar]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Gods of War (Manowar album)|Gods of War]]''\n* [[Marilyn Manson (band)|Marilyn Manson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Eat Me, Drink Me]]'' US #8 UK #8\n* [[Mayhem (band)|Mayhem]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ordo Ad Chao|Ordo ad Chao]]''\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[United Abominations]]'' US #8\n* [[Metalium]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nothing to Undo \u2013 Chapter Six]]''\n* [[Ministry (band)|Ministry]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Last Sucker]]''\n* [[Mountain (band)|Mountain]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Masters of War (album)|Masters of War]]''\n* [[Nightwish]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dark Passion Play]]''\n* [[Nile (band)|Nile]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ithyphallic (album)|Ithyphallic]]''\n* [[Nine Inch Nails]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Year Zero (album)|Year Zero]]'' US #2 UK #6\n* [[Otep]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Ascension (Otep album)|The Ascension]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Immortalis (album)|Immortalis]]''\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Black Rain (Ozzy Osbourne album)|Black Rain]]'' US #3 UK #10\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[In Requiem]]''\n* [[Poison (American band)|Poison]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Poison'd!]]''\n* [[Porcupine Tree]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fear of a Blank Planet]]''\n* [[Powerwolf]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lupus Dei]]''\n* [[Primal Fear (band)|Primal Fear]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[New Religion (album)|New Religion]]\"\n* [[Prong (band)|Prong]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Power of the Damager]]''\n* [[Queens of the Stone Age]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Era Vulgaris (album)|Era Vulgaris]]''\n* [[Queensr\u00ffche]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Take Cover (album)|Take Cover]]''\n* [[Rose Tattoo]]&nbsp;- ''Blood Brothers''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Snakes & Arrows]]'' US #3 CAN #3\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Inner Sanctum]]''\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Humanity: Hour I]]'' GER #9\n* [[Sevendust]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alpha (Sevendust album)|Alpha]]''\n* [[Sirenia (band)|Sirenia]]&nbsp;\u201