ags]]''\n* [[Daron Malakian and Scars on Broadway]]&nbsp;- ''[[Scars on Broadway (album)|Scars on Broadway]]''\n* [[Death Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Killing Season (album)|Killing Season]]''\n* [[Def Leppard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Songs from the Sparkle Lounge]]'' US #5 UK #10\n* [[Dir En Grey]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Uroboros (album)|Uroboros]]''\n* [[Disturbed (band)|Disturbed]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Indestructible (Disturbed album)|Indestructible]]'' US #1\n* [[Dokken]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lightning Strikes Again]]''\n* [[Double Dragon (band)|Double Dragon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Devastator''\n* [[DragonForce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ultra Beatdown]]''\n* [[Edguy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tinnitus Sanctus]]''\n* [[Eluveitie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Slania]]''\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]]&nbsp;- ''Thrash Speed Burn''\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bad for You Baby]]''\n* [[Girlschool]]&nbsp;- ''[[Legacy (Girlschool album)|Legacy]]''\n* [[Gojira (band)|Gojira]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Way of All Flesh (album)|The Way of All Flesh]]''\n* [[Guns N' Roses]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Chinese Democracy]]'' US #3 UK #2\n* [[Heidevolk]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Walhalla Wacht]]''\n* [[Iced Earth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Crucible of Man: Something Wicked Part 2|The Crucible of Man]]''\n* [[In Flames]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[A Sense of Purpose]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nostradamus (album)|Nostradamus]]''\n* [[King's X]]&nbsp;- ''[[XV (King's X album)|XV]]''\n* [[Korpiklaani]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Korven Kuningas]]''\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Metal Mad]]''\n* [[Metal Church]]&nbsp;- ''[[This Present Wasteland]]''\n* [[Metalium]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Incubus \u2013 Chapter Seven]]''\n* [[Metallica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Death Magnetic]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Melvins]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nude with Boots]]''\n* [[Meshuggah]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[obZen]]''\n* [[Michael Schenker Group]]&nbsp;- ''[[In the Midst of Beauty]]''\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Saints of Los Angeles]]'' US #4\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mot\u00f6rizer]