iferum]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Unsung Heroes (Ensiferum album)|Unsung Heroes]]''\n* [[Enslaved (band)|Enslaved]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[RIITIIR]]''\n* [[Epica (band)|Epica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Requiem for the Indifferent]]''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]]&nbsp;- ''[[Bag of Bones (album)|Bag of Bones]]''\n* [[The Faceless]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Autotheism (album)|Autotheism]]''\n* [[Fear Factory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Industrialist]]''\n* [[Flotsam and Jetsam (band)|Flotsam and Jetsam]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ugly Noise]]''\n* [[Freedom Call]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Land of the Crimson Dawn]]''\n* [[Goatwhore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blood for the Master]]''\n* [[Gojira (band)|Gojira]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[L'Enfant Sauvage (album)|L'Enfant Sauvage]]''\n* [[Hacktivist (band)|Hacktivist]]&nbsp;\u2013 Hacktivist (EP)\n* [[Halestorm]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Strange Case Of...]]''\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fanatic (Heart album)|Fanatic]]''\n* Heart of a Coward&nbsp;\u2013 Hope and Hinderance\n* [[Heidevolk]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Batavi (album)|Batavi]]''\n* [[Hellyeah]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Band of Brothers (Hellyeah album)|Band of Brothers]]\n* [[High on Fire]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[De Vermis Mysteriis (album)|De Vermis Mysteriis]]''\n* [[Huntress (band)|Huntress]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Spell Eater''\n* [[Job for a Cowboy]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Demonocracy]]''\n* [[Kamelot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Silverthorn (album)|Silverthorn]]''\n* [[Katatonia]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dead End Kings]]''\n* [[King's X]]&nbsp;- ''Burning Down Boston''\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Monster (Kiss album)|Monster]]'' US #3\n* [[Korpiklaani]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Manala (album)|Manala]]''\n* [[Kreator]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Phantom Antichrist]]'' GER #5\n* [[L.A. Guns]]&nbsp;- ''[[Hollywood Fever (album)|Hollywood Fever]]''\n* [[Lamb of God (band)|Lamb of God]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Resolution (Lamb of God album)|Resolution]]'' US #3\n* [[Linkin Park]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Living Things (Linkin Park album)|Living Things]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Lostprophets]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Weapons (al