e\"\n* [[Black Label Society]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[My Dying Time]]\"\n* [[Black Veil Brides]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Goodbye Agony\"\n* Black Veil Brides&nbsp;\u2013 \"Faithless\"\n* Black Veil Brides&nbsp;\u2013 \"Heart Of Fire\"\n* [[Body Count (band)|Body Count]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Talk Shit, Get Shot\"\n* [[Deathstars]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"All the Devil's Toys\"\n* [[Demon Hunter]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Artificial Light\"\n* [[Exodus (American band)|Exodus]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Salt the Wound\"\n* [[Five Finger Death Punch]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[House of the Rising Sun#Five Finger Death Punch version|House of the Rising Sun]]\"\n* Five Finger Death Punch&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Wrong Side of Heaven]]\"\n* [[Godsmack]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[1000hp (song)|1000hp]]\"\n* Godsmack&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Something Different (Godsmack song)|Something Different]]\"\n* Godsmack&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[What's Next? (Godsmack song)|What's Next?]]\"\n* [[In Flames]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Rusted Nail\"\n* In Flames&nbsp;\u2013 \"Through Oblivion\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Redeemer of Souls\"\n* Judas Priest&nbsp;\u2013 \"Halls of Valhalla\"\n* [[Machine Head (band)|Machine Head]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Now We Die\"\n* Machine Head&nbsp;\u2013 \"Killers & Kings\"\n* [[Mastodon (band)|Mastodon]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[High Road (Mastodon song)|High Road]]\"\n* Mastodon&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Motherload\"\n* [[Nothing More]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[This is the Time (Ballast)]]\"\n* Nothing More&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mr. MTV]]\"\n* [[Sabaton (band)|Sabaton]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"To Hell and Back\"\n* Sabaton&nbsp;\u2013 \"Resist and Bite\"\n* Sabaton&nbsp;\u2013 \"Night Witches\"\n* [[Slipknot (band)|Slipknot]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Killpop]]\"\n* Slipknot&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Negative One]]\"\n* Slipknot&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Devil In I]]\"\n* [[Sonata Arctica]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Wolves Die Young\"\n* Sonata Arctica&nbsp;\u2013 \"Cloud Factory\"\n* Sonata Arctica&nbsp;\u2013 \"Love\"\n* [[Steel Panther]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Burden of Being Wonderful\"\n* Steel Panther&nbsp;\u2013 \"Gloryhole\"\n* Steel Panther&nbsp;\u2013 \"Pussywhipped\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Angela Gossow]] leaves [[Arch Enemy]] but remains as the band's manager. She is replaced by [[Alissa White-Gluz]], former vocalist of [[The Agonist]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/angela-gossow-leaves-arch-enemy-new-singer-announced/|title=Angela Gossow Leaves Arch Enemy, New Singer Announced|publisher=Metal Hammer|date=2014-03-17|accessdate=2014-04-06|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321184702/http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/angela-gossow-leaves-arch-enemy-new-singer-announced/|archivedate=March 21, 2014|df=mdy-all}}</ref> On the same day, The Agonist have announced they have parted ways with Alissa and that Vicky Psarakis had taken over as their new vocalist.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metalinjection.net/latest-news/the-agonist-announce-new-vocalist|title=THE AGONIST Announce New Vocalist|publisher=Metal Injection|date=2014-03-17|accessdate=2014-04-06}}</ref>\n* Bassist [[Greg Christian]] leaves [[Testament (band)|Testament]]. He is replaced by former bassist, [[Steve DiGiorgio]] who played on the albums [[The Gathering (Testament album)|The Gathering]] and [[First Strike Still Deadly]]\n* [[Malcolm Young]] of [[AC/DC|ACDC]] has taken break from the band due to his illness. The Band posted a message to the fans that they will continue to make music again.\n* The remaining members of [[Lostprophets]] regroup as [[No Devotion]] with former [[Thursday (band)|Thursday]] and [[United Nations (band)|United Nations]] frontman [[Geoff Rickly]] joining the group as lead vocalist due to former frontman [[Ian Watkins (Lostprophets)|Ian Watkins]]' conviction on child sexual abuse.\n* [[Gwar]] frontman [[Dave Brockie]] dies of an accidental heroin overdose on March 23, 2014. The band formed the Dave Brockie Foundation.\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]] frontman [[Tim Lambesis]] is sentenced to 6 years in jail on May 16 for murder-for-hire.\n* [[Iced Earth]] cancel their Summer tour including their appearance at [[Wacken Open Air]] due to founding member [[Jon Schaffer]] requiring cervical fusion surgery.\n* [[Static-X]], frontman [[Wayne Static]], dies at 48 on November 1.\n* [[AC/DC]] drummer [[Phil Rudd]] is arrested on November 5 for murder-for-hire, drug possession and threatening to kill, murder-for-hire charge is dropped the next day but other charges remain.\n* Both [[Shawn Drover]] and [[Chris Broderick]] leave [[Megadeth]] in late November.\n\n==2015==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Dead Cross]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n*[[3 Inches of Blood]]\n*[[Mot\u00f6rhead]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Disturbed (band)|Disturbed]]\n* [[Evanescence]]\n* [[Breaking Benjamin]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[10 Years (band)|10 Years]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[From Birth to Burial]]''\n* [[Act of Defiance]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Birth and the Burial]]''\n* [[Amorphis]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Under the Red Cloud]]''\n* [[Angra (band)|Angra]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Secret Garden (album)|Secret Garden]]''\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Shadowmaker]]''\n* [[Armored Saint]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Win Hands Down (album)|Win Hands Down]]''\n* [[August Burns Red]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Found in Far Away Places]]'' US #9 CAN #7\n* [[Baroness (band)]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Purple (Baroness album)|Purple]]''\n* [[Battle Beast (band)|Battle Beast]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Unholy Savior]]'' FIN #1\n* [[Between the Buried and Me]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Coma Ecliptic]]''\n* [[Blind Guardian]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Beyond the Red Mirror]]'' GER #4\n* [[Bullet for My Valentine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Venom (Bullet for My Valentine album)|Venom]]'' US #8 UK #3 AUS #1\n* [[Chaos Divine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Colliding Skies''\n* [[Children of Bodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[I Worship Chaos]]''\n* [[Cradle of Filth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hammer of the Witches]]''\n* [[Def Leppard]]&nbsp;- ''[[Def Leppard (album)|Def Leppard]]''\n* [[Devil You Know (band)|Devil You Know]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[They Bleed Red]]''\n* [[Disturbed (band)|Disturbed]