2, [[Hellyeah]] and former [[Pantera]] and [[Damageplan]] drummer [[Vinnie Paul]] dies at the age of 54; he is the second member of Pantera and Damageplan to die, following his brother [[Dimebag Darrell]], who was shot 14 years earlier.<ref>{{cite web|title=Former PANTERA Drummer VINNIE PAUL Dead At 54|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/former-pantera-drummer-vinnie-paul-dead-at-54/|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|accessdate=June 22, 2018|date=June 22, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==2019==\n===Albums===\n* [[Allegaeon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Apoptosis (album)|Apoptosis]]''\n* [[Amon Amarth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Berserker (Amon Amarth album)|Berserker]]''\n* [[Anthem (band)|Anthem]]&nbsp;- ''Nucleus''\n* [[Arch Enemy]]&nbsp;- ''Covered In Blood''\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]&nbsp;- ''[[Shaped by Fire]]''\n* [[Babymetal]]&nbsp;- ''[[Metal Galaxy]]''\n* [[Band-Maid]]&nbsp;- ''[[Conqueror (Band-Maid album)|Conqueror]]''\n* [[Bloodbound]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Rise of the Dragon Empire''\n* [[Death Angel]]&nbsp;- ''[[Humanicide]]''\n* [[Destruction (band)|Destruction]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Born to Perish]]''\n* [[Dragonforce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Extreme Power Metal]]''\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;- ''[[Distance Over Time]]''\n* [[Eluveitie]]&nbsp;- ''[[Ategnatos]]''\n* [[Elvenking (band)|Elvenking]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Reader of the Runes \u2013 Divination''\n* [[Evergrey]]&nbsp;- ''The Atlantic''\n* [[Fleshgod Apocalypse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Veleno]]''\n* [[Freedom Call]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''M.E.T.A.L.''\n* [[Gloryhammer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Legends from Beyond the Galactic Terrorvortex]]''\n* [[Grand Magus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wolf God]]''\n* [[HammerFall]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dominion (HammerFall album)|Dominion]]''\n* [[I Prevail]]&nbsp;- ''[[Trauma (I Prevail album)|Trauma]]''\n* [[In Flames]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[I, the Mask]]''\n* [[Iris Official]] - ''[[Goliath\u2019s Throne]]''\n* [[Killswitch Engage]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Atonement (Killswitch Engage album)|Atonement]]''\n* [[Korn]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Nothing (Korn album)|The Nothing]]''\n* [[Mark Morton (musician)|Mark Morton]]&nbsp;- ''[[Anesthetic (album)|Anesthetic]]''\n* [[Motionless In White]]&nbsp;- ''[[Disguise (album)|Disguise]]''\n* [[Of Mice & Men (band)|Of Mice & Men]]&nbsp;- ''[[Earthandsky]]''\n* [[Opeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[In Cauda Venenum]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Wings of War]]''\n* [[Papa Roach]]&nbsp;- ''[[Who Do You Trust? (album)|Who Do You Trust?]]''\n* [[Possessed (band)|Possessed]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Revelations of Oblivion''\n* [[Rammstein]]&nbsp;- ''[[Untitled Rammstein album|Rammstein]]''\n* [[Rhapsody of Fire]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Eighth Mountain]]''\n* [[Sabaton (band)|Sabaton]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Great War (Sabaton album)|The Great War]]''\n* [[Slipknot (band)|Slipknot]]&nbsp;- ''[[We Are Not Your Kind]]''\n* [[Soilwork]]&nbsp;- ''[[Verkligheten]]''\n* [[Sonata Arctica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Talviy\u00f6]]''\n* [[Steel Panther]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Heavy Metal Rules]]''\n* [[Tool (band)|Tool]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fear Inoculum (album)|Fear Inoculum]]''\n* [[Turilli / Lione Rhapsody]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Zero Gravity (Rebirth and Evolution)]]''\n* [[Twilight Force]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dawn of the Dragonstar]]''\n* [[Visions of Atlantis]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Wanderers''\n* [[Within Temptation]]&nbsp;- ''[[Resist (Within Temptation album)|Resist]]''\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Allegaeon]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Stellar Tidal Disruption\"\n* Allegaeon&nbsp;\u2013 \"Extremophiles (B)\"\n* Allegaeon&nbsp;\u2013 \"Colors of the Currents\"\n* [[Amon Amarth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Raven's Flight\"\n* Amon Amarth&nbsp;\u2013 \"Crack the Sky\"\n* [[Babymetal]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Elevator Girl (song)|Elevator Girl]]\"\n* Babymetal&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Pa Pa Ya!!]]\"\n* [[Bloodbound]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Rise of the Dragon Empire\"\n* Bloodbound&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Warlock's Trail\"\n* [[Chaos Divine]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Unspoken\"\n* Chaos Divine&nbsp;\u2013 \"False Flags\"\n* [[Dragonforce]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Highway to Oblivion\"\n* Dragonforce&nbsp;\u2013 \"Heart De