ive Finger Death Punch]]&nbsp;- ''[[Living the Dream (Five Finger Death Punch song)|Living the Dream]]''\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;- ''[[Ordinary Man (Ozzy Osbourne song)|Ordinary Man]]''\n* Ozzy Osbourne&nbsp;- ''[[Under the Graveyard]]''\n* [[Poppy]]&nbsp;- ''[[Bloodmoney]]''\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]]&nbsp;- ''Children of the Next Level''\n* Testament&nbsp;- ''Night of the Witch''\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=note}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Timeline of heavy metal and hard rock music}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Timeline Of Heavy Metal Music}}\n[[Category:Timelines of heavy metal| ]]\n[[Category:Hard rock]]\n[[Category:Timelines of music]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=June 2013}}\nThis is a '''timeline of [[Heavy metal music|heavy metal]] and [[hard rock]]''', from its beginning in the early 1960s to the present time.\n{{Expand list|date=August 2011}}\n{{horizontal TOC|nonum=yes|limit=2}}\n\n==1960==\n===Newly formed band===\n* [[The Beatles]]\n\n==1961==\n===Newly formed band===\n* [[Golden Earring]]\n\n==1962==\n===Newly formed band===\n* [[The Rolling Stones]]\n\n==1964==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Alice Cooper (band)|Alice Cooper]]\n* [[The Amboy Dukes]]\n* [[The Kinks]]\n* [[Lynyrd Skynyrd]]\n* [[MC5]]\n* [[The Velvet Underground]]\n* [[The Who]]\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[The Kinks]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[You Really Got Me]]\"\n* The Kinks&nbsp;- \"[[All Day and All of the Night]]\"\n* [[Them (band)|Them]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Gloria (Them song)|Gloria]]\"\n\n==1965==\n===Newly formed bands===\n*[[13th Floor Elevators]]\n* [[The Doors]]\n* [[The Gods (band)|The Gods]]\n* [[The Guess Who]]\n*[[The Grateful Dead]]\n* [[Jefferson Airplane]]\n* [[Pink Floyd]]\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[The Rolling Stones]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[(I Can't Get No) Satisfaction]]\"\n* [[The Who]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[My Generation]]\"\n* [[The Beatles]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Day Tripper]]\"\n\n==1966==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Cream (band)|Cream]