Everybody]]\" {{small|([[Eddie Cochran]] cover)}}\n\n===Events===\n* [[Jimi Hendrix]] dies at 27 on September 18 in [[London|London, England]] from alcohol and [[barbiturate]] abuse.\n\n==1971==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Foghat]]\n* [[Pentagram (band)|Pentagram]]\n* [[Cirith Ungol (band)#Titanic|Titanic]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Iron Butterfly]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Love It to Death]]''\n* Alice Cooper&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Killer (Alice Cooper album)|Killer]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[April Wine (album)|April Wine]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Master of Reality]]'' US #8 UK #5\n* [[Bloodrock]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bloodrock 3]]''\n* [[Bloodrock]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bloodrock USA]]''\n* [[Blue Cheer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Oh! Pleasant Hope]]''\n* [[Breakout (band)|Breakout]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blues]]''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Budgie (album)|Budgie]]''\n* [[Cactus (American band)|Cactus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[One Way... or Another]]''\n* Cactus&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Restrictions (album)|Restrictions]]''\n* [[Caravan (band)|Caravan]]&nbsp;- ''[[In the Land of Grey and Pink]]''\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fireball (album)|Fireball]]'' UK #1\n* [[Dust (band)|Dust]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dust (Dust album)|Dust]]''\n* [[Grand Funk Railroad]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Survival (Grand Funk Railroad album)|Survival]]''\n* Grand Funk Railroad&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[E Pluribus Funk]]''\n* [[Humble Pie (band)|Humble Pie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rock On (Humble Pie album)|Rock On]]''\n* [[James Gang]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Thirds (album)|Thirds]]''\n* [[King Crimson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Islands (King Crimson album)|Islands]]''\n* [[Leaf Hound]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Growers of Mushroom]]''\n* [[Led Zeppelin]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Led Zeppelin IV|Untitled fourth album]]'' US #2 UK #1\n* [[Mountain (band)|Mountain]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nantucket Sleighride (album)|Nantucket Sleighride]]''\n* Mountain&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Flowers of Evil (album)|Flowers of Evil]]''\n* [[Steppenwolf (ba