gus]]''\n* [[Yes (band)|Yes]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Close to the Edge]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* ''[[Live (UFO album)|UFO Live]]''\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[School's Out (song)|School's Out]]\" US #7 UK #1\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Snowblind (Black Sabbath song)|Snowblind]]\"\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cities on Flame with Rock and Roll]]\"\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Highway Star (song)|Highway Star]]\"\n* Deep Purple&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Lazy (Deep Purple song)|Lazy]]\"\n* Deep Purple&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Smoke on the Water]]\" US #4\n* Deep Purple&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Space Truckin']]\"\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Paper Plane (song)|Paper Plane]]\"\n\n==1973==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[AC/DC]]\n* [[Cheap Trick]]\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]\n* [[Journey (band)|Journey]]\n* [[Kansas (band)|Kansas]]\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]\n* [[Montrose (band)|Montrose]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[The Doors]]\n* [[MC5]]\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]] (hiatus)\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Aerosmith (album)|Aerosmith]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Billion Dollar Babies]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* Alice Cooper&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Muscle of Love]]'' US #10\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Electric Jewels]]''\n* [[Bachman\u2013Turner Overdrive]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bachman\u2013Turner Overdrive (1973 album)]]''\n* [[Bachman\u2013Turner Overdrive]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bachman\u2013Turner Overdrive II]]''\n* [[Beck, Bogert & Appice]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Beck, Bogert & Appice (album)|Beck, Bogert & Appice]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sabbath Bloody Sabbath]]'' UK #4\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Tyranny and Mutation]]''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Never Turn Your Back on a Friend]]''\n* [[Buffalo (band)|Buffalo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Volcanic Rock (album)|Volcanic Rock]]''\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Who Do We Think We Are]]'' UK #4\n* [[Foghat]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Foghat (1973 