ose (band)|Montrose]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Space Station #5\"\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Caroline (Status Quo song)|Caroline]]\"\n* [[Pink Floyd]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Money (Pink Floyd song)|Money]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* UFO replaces [[Bernie Marsden]] with Scorpions guitarist [[Michael Schenker]]. [[Uli Jon Roth|Ulrich Roth]] takes Schenker's place in Scorpions.\n* Ian Gillan and Roger Glover leave Deep Purple, and are replaced by [[David Coverdale]] and [[Trapeze (band)|Trapeze]] bassist [[Glenn Hughes]].\n\n==1974==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Cheap Trick]]\n* [[Meat Loaf]]\n* [[Praying Mantis (band)|Praying Mantis]]\n* [[moxy (band)|moxy]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[The Moody Blues]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Blue Cheer]]\n* [[Iron Butterfly]]\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]\n* [[Steppenwolf (band)|Steppenwolf]]\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Get Your Wings]]''\n* [[Bad Company]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bad Company (album)|Bad Company]]'' US #1 UK #3 CAN #7\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Secret Treaties]]'' US #53 CAN #54\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[In for the Kill (Budgie album)|In for the Kill!]]''\n* [[Buffalo (band)|Buffalo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Only Want You For Your Body]]''\n* [[Deep Purple]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Burn (Deep Purple album)|Burn]]'' US #9 UK #3 (introduced Mk. III lineup with [[David Coverdale]] and [[Glenn Hughes]])\n* Deep Purple&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stormbringer (album)|Stormbringer]]'' UK #6\n* [[Grand Funk Railroad]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Shinin' On]]''\n* Grand Funk Railroad&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[All the Girls in the World Beware!!!]]''\n* [[Humble Pie (band)|Humble Pie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Thunderbox (album)|Thunderbox]]''\n* [[Iron Butterfly]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Scorching Beauty]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rocka Rolla]]''\n* [[King Crimson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Starless and Bible Black]]''\n* King Crimson&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Red (King Crimson album)|Red]]''\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]