 Mountain\"\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Fly by Night (Rush song)|Fly by Night]]\"\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Down Down]]\" UK #1\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Stranglehold (Ted Nugent song)|Stranglehold]]\"\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Let It Roll\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Alice Cooper]] disbands, lead singer Vincent Furnier has name legally changed to \"Alice Cooper\" and launches solo career.\n* Hawkwind bassist [[Lemmy]] is fired when a drug arrest causes him to miss tour dates. He subsequently forms Mot\u00f6rhead.\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]'s original drummer, Lucas Fox, leaves the band. He is replaced by Phil \"Philthy Animal\" Taylor.\n* [[Ritchie Blackmore]] leaves Deep Purple, and is replaced by ex-[[James Gang]] guitarist [[Tommy Bolin]].\n\n==1976==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Black Flag (band)|Black Flag]]\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]/Vow Wow\n* [[Diamond Head (English band)|Diamond Head]]\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]\n* [[Ratt]]\n* [[Rose Tattoo]]\n* [[Running Wild (band)|Running Wild]]\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]\n* [[Billy Idol]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Argent (band)|Argent]]\n* [[Deep Purple]]\n* [[Montrose (band)|Montrose]]\n* [[Steppenwolf (band)|Steppenwolf]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[High Voltage (1976 album)|High Voltage]]''\n* AC/DC&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap]]'' AUS #4\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rocks (Aerosmith album)|Rocks]]'' US #3\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Alice Cooper Goes to Hell]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Whole World's Goin' Crazy]]''\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Flyin' High (album)|Flyin' High]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Technical Ecstasy]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Agents of Fortune]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Bow Wow''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[If I Were Brittania I'd Waive the Rules]]''\n* [[Buffalo (band)|Buffalo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[