ng)|Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap]]\"\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dream On (Aerosmith song)|Dream On]]\" US #6 (re-issue)\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Back in the Saddle]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Last Child]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Rats in the Cellar]]\"\n* Aerosmith&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Walk This Way]]\" US #10 (re-issue)\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[(Don't Fear) The Reaper]]\"\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Magic Man]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Crazy on You]]\"\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dreamboat Annie (song)|Dreamboat Annie]]\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Victim of Changes (song)|Victim of Changes]]\"\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Beth (song)|Beth]]\" US #7\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Calling Dr. Love]]\"\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Detroit Rock City]]\"\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Flaming Youth (song)|Flaming Youth]]\"\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[God of Thunder (song)|God of Thunder]]\"\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Shout It Out Loud (Kiss song)|Shout It Out Loud]]\"\n* [[Rainbow (English band)|Rainbow]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Stargazer (Rainbow song)|Stargazer]]\"\n* Rainbow&nbsp;\u2013 \"Starstruck\"\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Free-for-All\"\n* [[Thin Lizzy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Jailbreak (Thin Lizzy song)|Jailbreak]]\"\n* Thin Lizzy&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Boys Are Back in Town]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* Guitarist \"Fast\" Eddie Clarke joins [[Mot\u00f6rhead]] and [[Larry Wallis]] leaves after a month.\n* [[Pat Travers]] promotes the [[air guitar]] phenomenon by giving out cardboard guitars at his London shows. Cardboard guitars later become a staple of [[new wave of British heavy metal]] audiences.\n\n==1977==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Angel Witch]]\n* [[Def Leppard]]\n* [[Ram Jam]]\n* [[Samson (band)|Samson]]\n* [[Trust (French band)|Trust]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[The Moody Blues]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Let There Be Rock]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Draw the Line (Aerosmith album)|Draw The Line