tage (Rainbow album)]]'' UK #7\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Let There Be Rock (song)|Let There Be Rock]]\"\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Barracuda (song)|Barracuda]]\"\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Diamonds & Rust (song)|Diamonds & Rust]]\"\n* [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Christine Sixteen]]\"\n* Kiss&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Love Gun (song)|Love Gun]]\"\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Warrior\"\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Sails of Charon\"\n* [[Ted Nugent]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cat Scratch Fever (song)|Cat Scratch Fever]]\"\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Lights Out\"\n* UFO&nbsp;\u2013 \"Too Hot To Handle\"\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Buffalo (band)|Buffalo]]\n\n===Events===\n* [[Alice Cooper]] undergoes treatment for alcoholism and begins a period of career decline.\n\n==1978==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]\n* [[Dokken]]\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]]\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]\n* [[Girlschool]]\n* Avatar/[[Savatage]]\n* [[T.S.O.L.]]\n* [[Tygers of Pan Tang]]\n* [[Whitesnake]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Blue Cheer]] (End of the first hiatus)\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Powerage]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[From the Inside (Alice Cooper album)|From the Inside]]''\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[First Glance]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Never Say Die!]]''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]]&nbsp;- ''Guarantee''\n* [[Budgie (band)|Budgie]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Impeckable]]''\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]&nbsp;- ''[[Double Vision (Foreigner album)|Double Vision]]''\n* [[Gary Moore]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Back on the Streets (Gary Moore album)|Back on the Streets]]''\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;- ''[[Gillan (album)|Gillan]]''\n* [[Heart (band)|Heart]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Magazine (Heart album)|Magazine]]''\n* Heart&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Dog & Butterfly (album)|Dog & Butterfly]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stained Class]]''\n* [[Judas Priest]]&nbsp;