ound]]'' UK #33\n* [[Tygers Of Pan Tang]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Crazy Nights (Tygers of Pan Tang album)|Crazy Nights]]'' UK #51\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Wild, the Willing and the Innocent]]'' UK #19\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fair Warning (Van Halen album)|Fair Warning]]'' UK #49\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[Welcome to Hell]]''\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Come an' Get It]]'' UK #2\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Number the Brave]]''\n* [[Y&T]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Earthshaker (album)|Earthshaker]]''\n\n===Film soundtracks===\n* Animated Film ''[[Heavy Metal (film)|Heavy Metal]]'' features [[Sammy Hagar]], [[Riggs (band)|Riggs]], [[Devo]], [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]], [[Cheap Trick]], [[Don Felder]], [[Donald Fagen]], [[Nazareth (band)|Nazareth]], [[Journey (band)|Journey]], [[Grand Funk Railroad]], [[Black Sabbath]], [[Trust (French band)|Trust]], and [[Stevie Nicks]].\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Double Trouble (Gillan album)|Double Trouble]]'' UK #12\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No Sleep 'til Hammersmith]]'' UK #1\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Exit...Stage Left]]'' UK #6\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[April Wine]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Just Between You and Me (April Wine song)|Just Between You And Me]]\" UK #52\n* [[Billy Squier]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Stroke]]\" UK #52\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Mob Rules]]\" UK #46\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Burnin' for You]]\" US #40; UK #76\n* [[Foreigner (band)|Foreigner]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Urgent (song)|Urgent]]\" UK #54\n* Foreigner&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Juke Box Hero]]\" UK #48\n* Foreigner&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Waiting For A Girl Like You]]\" UK #8\n* [[Gillan (band)|Gillan]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[No Laughing in Heaven]]\" UK #31\n* Gillan&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Nightmare (Gillan song)|Nightmare]]\" UK #36\n* [[Girlschool]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Hit and Run (Girlschool album)|Hit and Run]]\" UK #32\n* Girlschool&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Hit and Run (Girlschool 