 Attack]]'' UK #19\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Iron Fist (album)|Iron Fist]]'' UK #6\n* [[Picture (band)|Picture]]&nbsp;- ''Diamond Dreamer''\n* [[Rainbow (rock band)|Rainbow]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Straight Between the Eyes]]'' UK #5\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Restless Breed]]''\n* [[Robert Plant]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Pictures at Eleven]]'' UK #2\n* [[The Rods]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Wild Dogs (album)|Wild Dogs]]'' UK #75\n* [[Rose Tattoo]]&nbsp;- ''[[Scarred for Life (Rose Tattoo album)|Scarred for Life]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Signals (Rush album)|Signals]]'' UK #3\n* [[Sammy Hagar]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Standing Hampton]]'' UK #84\n* [[Samson (band)|Samson]]&nbsp;- ''[[Before the Storm (Samson album)|Before the Storm]]''\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blackout (Scorpions album)|Blackout]]'' UK #11\n* [[Spider (British band)|Spider]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rock 'n' Roll Gypsies (Spider album)|Rock 'n' Roll Gypsies]]'' UK #75\n* [[Status Quo (band)|Status Quo]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[1+9+8+2]]'' UK #1\n* [[Survivor (band)|Survivor]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Eye of the Tiger (album)|Eye of the Tiger]]'' UK #1\n* [[Tank (band)|Tank]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Filth Hounds of Hades]]'' UK #33\n* [[T.S.O.L.]]&nbsp;- ''[[Beneath the Shadows]]''\n* [[Twisted Sister]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Under the Blade]]'' UK #70\n* [[Tygers of Pan Tang]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Cage (Tygers of Pan Tang album)|The Cage]]'' UK #13\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mechanix (album)|Mechanix]]'' UK #8\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Abominog]]'' UK #34\n* [[Van Halen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Diver Down]]'' UK #36\n* [[Vandenberg (band)|Vandenberg]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Vandenberg (album)|Vandenberg]]''\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[Black Metal (Venom album)|Black Metal]]''\n* [[Whitesnake]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Saints & Sinners (Whitesnake album)|Saints & Sinners]]'' UK #9\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Twin Barrels Burning]]''\n* [[Witchfinder General (band)|Witchfinder 