[[Flotsam and Jetsam (band)|Flotsam and Jetsam]] is hired after auditions are held.\n* The success of [[Bon Jovi]]'s ''[[Slippery When Wet]]'' ushers in the era of [[glam metal]]. The album went on to sell 28 million copies worldwide, and is one of the best-selling albums of all time.\n* [[Monsters Of Rock Festival]] features Headliner [[Ozzy Osbourne]] with support from [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]], [[Def Leppard]], [[Mot\u00f6rhead]], [[Bad News (band)|Bad News]] and [[Warlock (band)|Warlock]].\n* [[Metal Hammer mag]] launches its first issue for the UK market, October 1986\n\n==1987==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Alchemist (band)|Alchemist]]\n* [[Alice in Chains]]\n* [[Apocrypha]]\n* [[Asphyx]]\n* [[Ass\u00fcck]]\n* [[Autopsy (band)|Autopsy]]\n* [[Cynic (band)|Cynic]]\n* [[Danzig (band)|Danzig]]\n* [[Deicide (band)|Deicide]]\n* [[Entombed (band)|Entombed]]\n* [[Extremoduro]]\n* [[Meshuggah]]\n* [[Ningen Isu]]\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]\n* [[Nocturnus]]\n* [[Porcupine Tree]]\n* [[Primordial (band)|Primordial]]\n* [[Reincidentes]]\n* [[Rollins Band]]\n* [[Rotting Christ]]\n* [[Samael (band)|Samael]]\n* [[Therion (band)|Therion]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Twisted Sister]]\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Vanilla Fudge]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Permanent Vacation (album)|Permanent Vacation]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Raise Your Fist and Yell]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Among the Living]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[I'm the Man (EP)|I'm the Man]]'' (EP)\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Strength of Steel]]''\n* [[Armored Saint]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Raising Fear]]''\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Under the Sign of the Black Mark]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Eternal Idol]]''\n* [[The Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Electric (The Cult album)|Electric]]'' UK #4\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Scream Bloody Gore]]''\n* [[Death Angel