er Magnet]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Monster Magnet (album)|Monster Magnet]]''\n* [[Pantera]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Cowboys from Hell]]''\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lost Paradise (album)|Lost Paradise]]''\n* [[Poison (American band)|Poison]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Flesh & Blood (Poison album)|Flesh & Blood]]''\n* [[Primus (band)|Primus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Frizzle Fry]]''\n* [[Prong (band)|Prong]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Beg to Differ]]''\n* [[Queensr\u00ffche]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Empire (Queensr\u00ffche album)|Empire]]'' US #7\n* [[Ratt]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Detonator (album)|Detonator]]''\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Privilege of Power]]''\n* [[Sadus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Swallowed in Black]]''\n* [[Samson (band)|Samson]]&nbsp;- ''Refugee''\n* [[Scorpions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Crazy World (Scorpions album)|Crazy World]]'' GER #1\n* [[Show-Ya]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hard Way]]''\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Seasons in the Abyss]]''\n* [[Slaughter (band)|Slaughter]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stick It to Ya]]''\n* [[Sodom (band)|Sodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Better Off Dead (album)|Better Off Dead]]''\n* [[Steppenwolf (band)|Steppenwolf]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rise & Shine (Steppenwolf album)|Rise & Shine]]''\n* [[Steve Vai]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Passion and Warfare]]''\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lights...Camera...Revolution!]]''\n* [[Tankard (band)|Tankard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Meaning of Life (Tankard album)|The Meaning of Life]]''\n* [[Tarantula (band)|Tarantula]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Kingdom of Lusitania''\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Souls of Black]]''\n* [[T.S.O.L.]]&nbsp;- ''[[Strange Love (T.S.O.L. album)|Strange Love]]''\n* [[Turbo (Polish band)|Turbo]]&nbsp;- ''[[Dead End (Turbo album)|Dead End]]''\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]&nbsp;- ''[[Vicious Rumors (Vicious Rumors album)|Vicious Rumors]]''\n* [[Y&T]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Ten (Y&T album)|Ten]]\"\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Death Angel]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fall from Grace (Death Angel album)|Fall from Grace]