ampires]]''\n* [[Loudness (band)|Loudness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[On the Prowl (album)|On the Prowl]]''\n* [[Yngwie J. Malmsteen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Yngwie Malmsteen Collection]]''\n* [[Melvins]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bullhead (album)|Bullhead]]''\n* [[Meshuggah]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Contradictions Collapse]]''\n* [[Metal Church]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Human Factor (album)|The Human Factor]]''\n* [[Metallica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Metallica (album)|Metallica]]'' US #1 UK #1\n* [[Monster Magnet]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Spine of God]]''\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Decade of Decadence]]'' US #2\n* [[Mot\u00f6rhead]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[1916 (album)|1916]]''\n* [[Mr. Big (band)|Mr. Big]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Lean into It]]''\n* [[Mr. Bungle]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Mr. Bungle (album)|Mr. Bungle]]''\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nevermind]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Horrorscope (Overkill album)|Horrorscope]]''\n* [[Ozzy Osbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No More Tears]]'' US #7\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Gothic (Paradise Lost album)|Gothic]]''\n* [[Pearl Jam]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ten (Pearl Jam album)|Ten]]''\n* [[Praying Mantis (band)|Praying Mantis]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Predator in Disguise''\n* [[Primus (band)|Primus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Sailing the Seas of Cheese]]''\n* [[Prong (band)|Prong]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Prove You Wrong]]''\n* [[Queen (band)|Queen]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Innuendo]]'' UK #1\n* [[Running Wild (band)|Running Wild]]&nbsp;- ''[[Blazon Stone]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Roll the Bones]]'' US #3 UK #10\n* [[Savatage]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Streets: A Rock Opera]]''\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Solid Ball of Rock]]''\n* [[Sepultura]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Arise (Sepultura album)|Arise]]''\n* [[Skid Row (American band)|Skid Row]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Slave to the Grind]]'' US #1\n* [[Soundgarden]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Badmotorfinger]]''\n* [[Type O Negative]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Slow, Deep and Hard]]''\n* [[Uriah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]