ican band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Nothing\"\n* [[Arch Enemy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Bury Me an Angel\"\n* [[Helloween]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Time of the Oath (song)|The Time of the Oath]]\"\n* Helloween&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Power (Helloween song)|Power]]\"\n* [[Iced Earth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"I Died For You\"\n* [[Marilyn Manson]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Beautiful People (song)|The Beautiful People]]\"\n* Marilyn Manson&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Tourniquet (Marilyn Manson song)|Tourniquet]]\"\n* [[Metallica]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Bleeding Me]]\"\n* [[Pantera]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Drag the Waters]]\"\n* [[Rage Against the Machine]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Bulls on Parade]]\"\n* [[Savatage]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"One Child\n* [[Sepultura]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Roots Bloody Roots]]\"\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Gemini\"\n* [[Therion (band)|Therion]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"To Mega Therion\"\n* [[Tool (band)|Tool]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Stinkfist]]\"\n\n==1997==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[2wo]]\n* [[Alien Crime Syndicate]]\n* [[American Head Charge]]\n* [[Atargatis (band)|Atargatis]]\n* [[The Dillinger Escape Plan]]\n* [[Dir En Grey]]\n* [[Disturbed (band)|Disturbed]]\n* [[Elvenking (band)|Elvenking]]\n* [[Finntroll]]\n* [[Hardcore Superstar]]\n* [[Isis (band)|Isis]]\n* [[Hate Eternal]]\n* [[Lostprophets]]\n* [[Nonpoint]]\n* [[Pig Destroyer]]\n* [[Primal Fear (band)|Primal Fear]]\n* [[Soulfly]]\n* [[Spawn of Possession]]\n* [[Turisas]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Allegiance (Australian band)|Allegiance]]\n* [[Prong (band)|Prong]]\n* [[Soundgarden]]\n* [[Skindred]]\n* [[X Japan]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nine Lives (Aerosmith album)|Nine Lives]]'' US #1 UK #4\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Absolutely No Alternative]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Magic (Axel Rudi Pell album)|Magic]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Reunion (Black Sabbath album)|Reunion]]''\n* [[Body Count (band)|Body Count]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Violent Demise: The Last Days]]''\n* [[Bruce Dickinson]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Accident of Birth