ium]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Crusade (album)|The Crusade]]'' UK #7\n* [[Twisted Sister]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[A Twisted Christmas]]''\n* [[T\u00fdr (band)|T\u00fdr]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ragnarok (T\u00fdr album)|Ragnarok]]''\n* [[UFO (band)|UFO]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Monkey Puzzle (UFO album)|The Monkey Puzzle]]''\n* [[Underoath]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Define the Great Line]]'' US #2\n* [[Unearth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[III: In the Eyes of Fire]]''\n* [[Venom (band)|Venom]]&nbsp;- ''[[Metal Black]]''\n* [[Vicious Rumors]]&nbsp;- ''[[Warball]]''\n* [[Wishbone Ash]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Clan Destiny]]''\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Children of Bodom]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Chaos Ridden Years&nbsp;\u2013 Stockholm Knockout Live]]''\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Holy Diver&nbsp;\u2013 Live]]''\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Score (Dream Theater album)|Score]]''\n* [[Gigantour (album)|Gigantour]] (The album features performances by [[Megadeth]], [[Dream Theater]], Anthrax, [[Fear Factory]], [[Life of Agony]], [[Nevermore]], [[Dry Kill Logic]], [[Symphony X]] and [[Bobaflex]])\n* [[Rainbow (English band)|Rainbow]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live in Munich 1977]]''\n* [[Rush (band)|Rush]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Grace Under Pressure Tour (album)|Grace Under Pressure Tour]]''\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Eagle Has Landed&nbsp;\u2013 part 3|The Eagle Has Landed&nbsp;\u2013 Part III]]''\n* [[Nightwish]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[End of an Era (album)]]''\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Avenged Sevenfold]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Beast and the Harlot]]\"\n* Avenged Sevenfold&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Burn It Down (Avenged Sevenfold song)|Burn It Down]]\"\n* [[Deftones]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Hole in the Earth]]\"\n* Deftones&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Mein (song)|Mein]]\"\n* [[Dir En Grey]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Agitated Screams of Maggots]]\"\n* [[DragonForce]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Through the Fire and Flames]]\"\n* [[Edguy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Superheroes (EP)|Superheroes]]\"\n* [[Fear Factory]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Transgression\"\n* [[Godsmack]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Speak 