og (band)|Cog]] (until 2016)\n* [[Despised Icon]]\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]] (Due to [[Ronnie James Dio]]'s death)\n* [[Heaven & Hell (band)|Heaven & Hell]]\n* [[The Number Twelve Looks Like You]]\n* [[Revolution Renaissance]]\n* [[Static-X]]\n* [[Type O Negative]] (Due to [[Peter Steele]]'s death)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[A Perfect Circle]]\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[AC/DC]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Iron Man 2 (soundtrack)]]'' US #4 UK #1 AUS #2\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Blood of the Nations]]'' GER #4\n* [[After the Burial]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[In Dreams (After the Burial album)|In Dreams]]\n* [[Agalloch]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Marrow of the Spirit]]''\n* [[Airbourne (band)|Airbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[No Guts. No Glory.]]''\n* [[All That Remains (band)|All That Remains]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[For We Are Many]]'' US #10\n* [[Aqua_(Angra_album)|Angra - Aqua]]\n* [[Apocalyptica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[7th Symphony (album)|7th Symphony]]''\n* [[Armored Saint]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[La Raza (album)|La Raza]]''\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Powerless Rise]]'' US #10\n* [[Avantasia]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Wicked Symphony]]''\n* [[Avantasia]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Angel of Babylon]]''\n* [[Avenged Sevenfold]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nightmare (Avenged Sevenfold album)|Nightmare]]'' US #1 UK #5\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Crest (album)|The Crest]]''\n* [[Bad City]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Welcome to the Wasteland (Bad City album)|Welcome to the Wasteland]]''\n* [[Battlecross]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Push Pull Destroy''\n* [[Black Label Society]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Order of the Black]]'' US #4\n* [[Black Veil Brides]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[We Stitch These Wounds]]\"\n* [[Bring Me the Horizon]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[There Is a Hell Believe Me I've Seen It. There Is a Heaven Let's Keep It a Secret.]]'' AUS #1\n* [[Bullet for My Valentine]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Fever (Bullet for My Valentine album)|Fever]]'' US #3 UK #5\n* [[Cradle of Filth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Darkly, Darkly, Venus A