ions (band)|Scorpions]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Live 2011: Get Your Sting & Blackout''\n* [[Sonata Arctica]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live in Finland]]''\n\n===Extended plays===\n* [[Black Veil Brides]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Rebels (EP)|Rebels]]''\n* [[Halestorm]]&nbsp;- ''[[Reanimate: The Covers EP]]''\n\n===Popular songs===\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Fight 'Em 'Til You Can't]]\"\n* [[Chevelle (band)|Chevelle]]&nbsp;- \"[[Face to the Floor]]\"\n* Chevelle&nbsp;- \"[[Hats Off to the Bull (song)|Hats Off to the Bull]]\n* [[Dream Theater]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[On the Backs of Angels]]\"\n* [[Falling In Reverse]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Drug In Me Is You]]\"\n* Falling In Reverse&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[I'm Not A Vampire]]\"\n* [[Five Finger Death Punch]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Under and Over It]]\"\n* Five Finger Death Punch&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Remember Everything]]\"\n* [[HammerFall]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[One More Time (HammerFall song)|One More Time]]\"\n* [[Iced Earth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Dystopia (Iced Earth song)|Dystopia]]\"\n* [[Korn]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Get Up! (Korn song)|Get Up!]]\"\n* Korn&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Narcissistic Cannibal]]\"\n* [[Mastodon (band)|Mastodon]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Curl of the Burl]]\"\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Public Enemy No. 1 (Megadeth song)|Public Enemy No. 1]]\"\n* [[Nightwish]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Storytime (song)|Storytime]]\"\n* [[Staind]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Eyes Wide Open (Staind song)|Eyes Wide Open]]\"\n* Staind&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Not Again (song)|Not Again]]\"\n* [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[In Waves (song)|In Waves]]\"\n* Trivium&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Built to Fall]]\"\n* [[Within Temptation]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Faster (Within Temptation song)|Faster]]\"\n* Within Temptation&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Sin\u00e9ad (Within Temptation song)|Sin\u00e9ad]]\"\n* Within Temptation&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Shot in the Dark (Within Temptation song)|Shot in the Dark]]\"\n\n===Events===\n* [[Helloween]] founder [[Kai Hansen]] of [[Gamma Ray (band)|Gamma Ray]] joins ex-[[Helloween]] vocalist [[Michael Kiske]] in his new band [[Unisonic (band)|Unisonic]].\n* On August 17 founding [[Rhapsody of Fire]] guitarist [[Luca Turilli]] leaves the band and as a friendly split decides to start his own Rhapsody band under the name [[Luca Turilli's Rhapsody]].\n\n==2012==\n\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Ashes of Ares]]\n* [[Black Star Riders]]\n* [[Devil You Know (band)|Devil You Know]]\n* [[Greta Van Fleet]]\n* [[Kaleo (band)|Kaleo]]\n* [[Massive (band)|Massive]]\n* [[Newsted]]\n* [[Seven Deadly]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Double Dragon (band)|Double Dragon]]\n* [[Staind]] (until 2014)\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Metal Church]]\n* [[Static-X]] \u2013 Wayne Static and his solo band got rights to the name and converted the solo band to Static-X\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Stalingrad (Accept album)|Stalingrad]]'' GER #6\n* [[Adrenaline Mob]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Omert\u00e0 (album)|Omert\u00e0]]''\n* [[Aerosmith]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Music from Another Dimension!]]''\n* [[Anaal Nathrakh]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Vanitas (Anaal Nathrakh album)|Vanitas]]''\n* [[Angel Witch]]&nbsp;- ''[[As Above, So Below (Angel Witch album)|As Above, So Below]]''\n* [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Awakened (album)|Awakened]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Circle of the Oath]]''\n* [[Baroness (band)|Baroness]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Yellow & Green (Baroness album)|Yellow & Green]]''\n* [[Becoming the Archetype]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[I Am (Becoming The Archetype album)|I Am]]''\n* [[Between the Buried and Me]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Parallax II: Future Sequence]]''\n* [[Cannibal Corpse]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Torture (album)|Torture]]''\n* [[Cattle Decapitation]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Monolith of Inhumanity]]''\n* [[Circus Maximus (Norwegian band)|Circus Maximus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Nine (Circus Maximus album)|Nine]]''\n* [[Converge (band)|Converge]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[All We Love We Leave Behind]]''\n* [[Cradle of Filth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Manticore and Other Horrors]]''\