ctory]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Soul Hacker\"\n* Fear Factory&nbsp;\u2013 \"Protomech\"\n* Fear Factory&nbsp;\u2013 \"Dielectric\"\n* [[Five Finger Death Punch]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Jekyll and Hyde (song)|Jekyll and Hyde]]\"\n* [[Ghost (Swedish band)|Ghost]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cirice]]\"\n* [[Gloryhammer]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Rise of the Chaos Wizards\"\n* [[Halestorm]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Apocalyptic (song)|Apocalyptic]]\"\n* [[Kamelot]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Insomnia\"\n* [[Lamb of God (band)|Lamb of God]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Still Echoes\"\n* Lamb of God&nbsp;\u2013 \"512\"\n* [[Leaves' Eyes]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Halvdan the Black\"\n* [[Leaves' Eyes]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Waking Eye\"\n* [[Lindemann (band)|Lindemann]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Praise Abort\"\n* [[Marilyn Manson (band)|Marilyn Manson]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Third Day of a Seven Day Binge]]\"\n* Marilyn Manson&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Deep Six (song)]]\"\n* Marilyn Manson&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Cupid Carries a Gun]]\"\n* Marilyn Manson&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[The Mephistopheles of Los Angeles]]\"\n* [[Megadeth]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Fatal Illusion\"\n* Megadeth&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Threat is Real\"\n* [[Nightwish]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[\u00c9lan (song)|\u00c9lan]]\"\n* Nightwish&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Endless Forms Most Beautiful (song)|Endless Forms Most Beautiful]]\"\n* [[Nothing More]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Jenny (Nothing More song)|Jenny]]\"\n* [[Papa Roach]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Face Everything and Rise (song)|Face Everything and Rise]]\"\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"No Hope in Sight\"\n* Paradise Lost&nbsp;\u2013 \"Beneath Broken Earth\"\n* [[Parkway Drive]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Crushed\"\n* [[Periphery (band)|Periphery]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Alpha\"\n* Periphery&nbsp;\u2013 \"Psychoshere\"\n* Periphery&nbsp;\u2013 \"Stranger Things\"\n* Periphery&nbsp;\u2013 \"The Bad Thing\"\n* [[Powerwolf]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Army of the Night]]\"\n* [[Slayer]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Repentless\"\n* Slayer&nbsp;\u2013 \"When the Stillness Comes\"\n* [[Slipknot (band)|Slipknot]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Killpop]]\"\n* [[Soulfly]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[We Sold Our Souls to Metal]]\"\n* [[Stratovarius]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Shine in the Dark\"\n* Stratovarius&nbsp;\u2013 \"My Eternal Dream\"\n* [[Symphony X]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Nevermore\"\n* Symphony X&nbsp;\u2013 \"Without You\"\n* [[Three Days Grace]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Painkiller (Three Days Grace song)|Painkiller]]\"\n* Three Days Grace&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[I Am Machine]]\"\n* Three Days Grace&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Human Race (Three Days Grace song)|Human Race]]\"\n* [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Silence in the Snow\"\n* Trivium&nbsp;\u2013 \"Blind Leading the Blind\"\n* Trivium&nbsp;\u2013 \"Until the World Goes Cold\"\n\n===Events===\n* On April 7, [[Iced Earth]] announced following a period of inactivity due to founding member [[Jon Schaffer]]'s cervical fusion surgery that the band would begin writing for their 12th studio album tentatively titled ''The Judas Goat'' and that drummer Brent Smedley would rejoin the band.\n* On April 20, [[AC/DC]] drummer [[Phil Rudd]] pleaded guilty to threat to kill and drug charges, though one threat to kill charge is dropped.\n* In April, soon after Phil Rudd pleaded guilty to threat to kill and drug charges, [[AC/DC]] announced [[Chris Slade]] as the band's official drummer.\n* On May 1, former [[Static-X]] bassist [[Tony Campos]] leaves [[Soulfly]] and joins [[Fear Factory]] replacing bassist [[Matt DeVries]].\n* On June 23, Disturbed unexpectedly announce their reunion after going on hiatus in 2011.\n* On July 9, Phil Rudd is sentenced to an eight month period of house arrest.\n* On July 19, Phil Rudd is arrested again after breaching the terms of his house arrest sentence.\n* On July 21, After the Burial guitarist Justin Lowe was found dead aged 32 after going missing. He previously made a public statement which displayed signs of mental instability.\n* On July 23, Avenged Sevenfold parts ways with drummer of four years Arin Ilejay citing musical differences.\n* On November 13, Mot\u00f6rhead drummer, Phil 'Animal' Taylor passes away.\n* On December 28, Mot\u00f6rhead founder and frontman Lemmy Kilimister dies from cancer. On the following day, the band announced that they would break up.\n\n==2016==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Invidia (band)|Invidia]]\n* [[Lovebites (band)|Lovebites]]\n* [[Prophets of Rage]]\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Agalloch]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://noisey.vice.com/en_us/article/agalloch-breakup-2016|title=A Requiem for Agalloch: 1995\u20132016|publisher=noisey.vice.com|accessdate=May 13, 2016}}</ref>\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.motley.com/news/|title=M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce's Final Tour|publisher=Motley.com|accessdate=October 7, 2014}}</ref>\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[Cog (band)|Cog]]\n* [[The Number Twelve Looks Like You]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Airbourne (band)|Airbourne]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Breakin' Outta Hell]]''\n* [[Alcest]] \u2013 ''[[Kodama (album)|Kodama]]''\n* [[Amaranthe]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Maximalism (album)|Maximalism]]''\n* [[Amon Amarth]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Jomsviking (album)|Jomsviking]]'' GER #1\n* [[Anaal Nathrakh]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Whole of the Law]]''\n* [[Animals as Leaders]] \u2013 ''[[The Madness of Many]]''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[For All Kings]]'' US #9\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]]&nbsp;- ''[[Anvil is Anvil]]''\n* [[Arch Enemy]] \u2013 ''[[War Eternal]]''\n* [[Avantasia]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ghostlights]]''\n* [[Avenged Sevenfold]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[The Stage (album)|The Stage]]''\n* [[Axel Rudi Pell]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Game of Sins (Axel Rudi Pell album)|Game of Sins]]''\n* [[Babymetal]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Metal Resistance]]''\n* [[Brujeria (band)|Brujeria]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Pocho Aztlan]]''\n* [[Cactus (American band)|Cactus]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Black Dawn (album)|Black Dawn]]''\n* [[Chevelle (band)|Chevelle]]&nbsp;- ''[[The North Corridor]]''\n* [[The Cult]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Hidden City (album)|Hidden City]]''\n* [[A Day to Remember]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Bad Vibrations]]'' US #2 UK #6 AUS #1\n* [[