time... Tour]].\n* On April 16, guitarist [[Angus Young]] of [[AC/DC]] joined [[Guns N' Roses]] on stage at Coachella to announce [[Axl Rose]] as AC/DC's new lead singer for the remainder of the [[Rock or Bust World Tour]] and beyond.\n* On May 7, marked the debut of [[Axl Rose]] as [[AC/DC]]'s new lead singer.\n* On September 19, bassist [[Cliff Williams]] of [[AC/DC]] released a video formally announcing his retirement from the music industry. Angus later clarified the band will continue with a new bassist and [[Axl Rose]] remaining as lead singer.\n\n==2017==\n===Newly formed bands===\n* [[Bad Wolves]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metalsucks.net/2017/11/03/bad-wolves-ex-devildriver-god-forbid-divine-heresy-sign-record-deal-release-new-single/|title=Bad Wolves (ex-DevilDriver, God Forbid, Divine Heresy) Sign Record Deal, Release New Single \u2013 MetalSucks|date=November 3, 2017|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.riffrelevant.com/2017/04/18/tommy-vext-westfield-massacre-ex-divine-heresy-share-video-teaser/|title=Tommy Vext (Westfield Massacre, Ex-Divine Heresy) & Doc Coyle (God Forbid, Vagus Nerve) Unite In BAD WOLVES; Share Video Teaser|date=April 18, 2017|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/bad-wolves-feat-former-devildriver-god-forbid-divine-heresy-members-lyric-video-for-toast-to-the-ghost-song/|title=BAD WOLVES Feat. Former DEVILDRIVER, GOD FORBID, DIVINE HERESY Members: Lyric Video For 'Toast To The Ghost' Song|date=November 3, 2017|publisher=}}</ref>\n* [[Powerflo]]\n* [[Exit Eden]]\n* Fireburn<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metalinjection.net/av/new-music/nails-ex-bad-brains-danzig-members-form-hardcore-band-fireburn|title=NAILS, Ex-BAD BRAINS & DANZIG Members Form Hardcore Band FIREBURN|date=August 9, 2017|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theprp.com/2017/08/08/news/fireburn-nails-ex-bad-brainsdanzig-etc-stream-debut-ep-dont-stop-youth/|title=Fireburn (Nails, Ex-Bad Brains/Danzig, Etc.) Stream Debut EP \"Don't Stop The Youth\" - Theprp.com|date=August 8, 2017|publisher=}}</ref>\n* The Fever<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bringthenoise.com/blog/jason-butlers-new-supergroup-the-fever-have-just|title=Jason Butler\u2019s New Supergroup The Fever Have Just Dropped A Massive New Single \"We\u2019re Coming In\" / the NOISE|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.upsetmagazine.com/news/fever-jason-aalon-butlers-new-band-btw-dropped-debut-single-coming/|title=Jason Aalon Butler's new band The Fever have dropped their debut single 'We're Coming In' \u2013 Upset|date=August 14, 2017|publisher=}}</ref>\n* Spiritbox<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bringthenoise.com/blog/iwrestledabearonces-courtney-laplante-and-michael|title=Iwrestledabearonce\u2019s&nbsp;Courtney LaPlante and Michael Stringer Reveal New Band Spiritbox, Debut New Single \"The Beauty Of Suffering\" / the NOISE|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n===Disbandments===\n* [[Black Sabbath]]\n* Mumakil (Switzerland [[grindcore]]), [[Relapse Records]]\n* Kronos (France [[grindcore]]), [[Deeds of Flesh|Unique Leader Records]]\n* [[The Dillinger Escape Plan]]\n* [[Trap Them]]\n* [[Spawn of Possession]]\n* [[Weekend Nachos]]\n* [[Your Memorial]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://facedownrecords.com/2017/05/10/your-memorial-announce-new-album-final-show/|title=YOUR MEMORIAL ANNOUNCE NEW ALBUM, FINAL SHOW \u2013 Facedown Records|website=facedownrecords.com}}</ref>\n\n===Reformed bands===\n* [[The Number Twelve Looks Like You]]\n\n===Albums===\n* [[Aldious]] \u2013 ''Unlimited Diffusion''\n* [[Alestorm]] \u2013 ''[[No Grave But the Sea]]''\n* [[Band-Maid]] \u2013 ''[[Just Bring It (album)|Just Bring It]]''\n* [[DragonForce]] \u2013 ''[[Reaching Into Infinity]]''\n* [[Ensiferum]] \u2013 ''[[Two Paths (album)|Two Paths]]''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]]&nbsp;- ''[[Walk the Earth]]''\n* [[Exit Eden]] \u2013 [[Rhapsodies in Black (album)|Rhapsodies in Black]]\n* [[Firewind]] \u2013 ''[[Immortals (album)|Immortals]]''\n* [[Iced Earth]] \u2013 ''[[Incorruptible (album)|Incorruptible]]''\n* [[In This Moment]] \u2013 ''[[Ritual (In This Moment album)|Ritual]]''\n* [[Ithilien (band)|Ithilien]] \u2013 ''Shaping the Soul''\n* [[Kobra and the Lotus]] \u2013 ''[[Prevail I]]''\n* [[Kreator]] \u2013 ''[[Gods of Violence]]''\n* [[L.A. Guns]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Missing Peace (album)|The Missing Peace]]''\n* [[Lovebites (band)|Lovebites]] \u2013 ''[[Awakening from Abyss]]''\n* [[Mastodon (band)|Mastodon]] \u2013 ''[[Emperor of Sand]]'' US #7\n* [[Melvins]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[A Walk with Love & Death]]''\n* [[Motionless in White]]&nbsp;- ''[[Graveyard Shift (album)|Graveyard Shift]]''\n* [[Nocturnal Rites]] \u2013 ''[[Phoenix (Nocturnal Rites album)|Phoenix]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]] \u2013 ''[[The Grinding Wheel]]''\n* [[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]] \u2013 ''[[Medusa (Paradise Lost album)|Medusa]]''\n* [[Queens of the Stone Age]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Villains (Queens of the Stone Age album)|Villains]]''\n* [[Quiet Riot]] \u2013 ''Road Rage''\n* [[Satyricon (band)|Satyricon]] \u2013 ''[[Deep Calleth Upon Deep]]''\n* [[Seether]] \u2013 ''[[Poison the Parish]]''\n* [[Sepultura]] \u2013 ''[[Machine Messiah (album)|Machine Messiah]]''\n* [[Show-Ya]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Aurora''\n* [[Suffocation (band)|Suffocation]] \u2013 ''[[...Of the Dark Light]]''\n* [[Steel Panther]] \u2013 ''[[Lower the Bar]]''\n* [[Tankard (band)|Tankard]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[One Foot in the Grave (Tankard album)|One Foot in the Grave]]''\n* [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]]&nbsp;- ''[[The Sin and the Sentence]]''\n* [[T.S.O.L.]]&nbsp;- ''The Trigger Complex''\n* [[While She Sleeps]] \u2013 ''[[You Are We]]'' UK #8\n\n===Live albums===\n* [[Babymetal]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Live at Tokyo Dome]]''\n\n===Popular songs===\n*[[Alestorm]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Alestorm\"\n*Alestorm&nbsp;\u2013 \"Mexico\"\n*[[DragonForce]]&nbsp;\u2013 \"Judgement Day\"\n*DragonForce&nbsp;\u2013 \"Curse of Darkness\"\n*DragonForce&nbsp;\u2013 \"[[Ashes of the Dawn]]\"\n*DragonForce&nbsp;\u2013 \